Sine Mora Ex;Sine Mora Ex;Sine Mora Ex;;videos\Sine Mora Ex (2017).mp4;OK;images\Sine Mora Ex (2017).webp;;Amazon;;THQ Nordic;31/07/2017;Sine Mora EX is a side-scrolling shoot'em up that provides a unique challenge, where time is the ultimate factor. Mixing classic shooter sensibilities with contemporary presentation, Sine Mora is a gorgeous shoot'em up offering both a Story Mode that weaves an over-the-top tale and an Arcade Mode that provides deep, satisfying gameplay to challenge fans of the genre. The story mode can be also played in local co-op mode.;;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/606730/97009/e4bb13d573e8c70f9fd5f0566baf5b4cf20c914a/1751108398/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1684232491;amazon_22c10eeb-6b68-4b49-a025-e36af43f0bbf;steam_606730;gog_2001892744;xboxone_528264958;psn_CUSA08149_00;psn_CUSA08076_00;test_CUSA08149_00;humble_sinemora_ex_row_steam;psx_Sine Mora EX;amazon_22c10eeb-6b68-4b49-a025-e36af43f0bbf;twitch_22c10eeb-6b68-4b49-a025-e36af43f0bbf;test_c42373ffc799bb7476eb079426227fc24572dd67;3ds_22c10eeb-6b68-4b49-a025-e36af43f0bbf;test_e4c5d3f4a989ea4cee4a879c7552c8bb62180d87;test_d5a02c7abb0599ce3a4cf5a0218fd6d270edb2d6;test_150f40fda4b53ee00a683b655bc1cd4f48c2718f;fanatical_sine-mora-ex;nswitch_01002820036A8000;test_7b82dcf719f5306c0102355c23db38e9e6f5aa98;test_708b1d76cecabec0e9bdde4357bbf1a581d4ab37;test_d769a9f95aea990c51b6c18122ce257fdf954c06;epic_e1b6cc682dd34a5f8fb467ea0344b8e1;test_a92b9c04d18cc500f1d8c28b963e5dc999ef1ece;test_59a6913c3e363d6662d429eee4e342f456104837;amazon_42bc18df-611f-d6c5-9dbb-44a0a94a6518;generic_51154202034907535;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
