Hue;Hue;Hue;;videos\Hue (2016).mp4;OK;images\Hue (2016).webp;;Amazon, Epic Games Store;Fiddlesticks;Curve Digital;30/08/2016;"Hue is a stark puzzle platformer where you shift the hue of the world, creating rifts when colours collide.

In this world, everyone sees in grayscale. Anne, a researcher specialising in colour theory, has created a mysterious ring which grants the ability to perceive and alter colour. After a fracas with her research assistant, she disappears into a coloured void. You play as Hue, Anne’s son, as he discovers fragments of his missing mother’s research and learns to perceive and alter colour for the first time.";Adventure, Indie, Platform, Puzzle;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/383270/70869/ea8a359eb9aa986069c1bb2ee51fa008bcd4ba8e/1750522028/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1474553838;amazon_2ebae692-5e13-4ee1-a4bd-1f901bac77c6, epic_Herring;steam_383270;xboxone_722916288;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0003307;psn_CUSA05065_00;psn_CUSA05091_00;amazon_2ebae692-5e13-4ee1-a4bd-1f901bac77c6;humble_2ebae692-5e13-4ee1-a4bd-1f901bac77c6;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0003659;twitch_2ebae692-5e13-4ee1-a4bd-1f901bac77c6;xboxone_1733126923;humble_hue_yogscast_steam;psvita_CUSA05091_00;humble_hue_steam;test_CUSA05091_00;3ds_2ebae692-5e13-4ee1-a4bd-1f901bac77c6;test_CUSA05065_00;epic_Herring;test_Herring;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0003307@subscription;humble_hue_bundle_steam;test_9a2534ed09162bd19c7196e272768b9a6753d300;test_6fb7198ce41a8af33f8e2af3615fd84bcc5c2433;test_gfn_383270;amazon_525d38d0-9972-4e26-a17e-c4b4ffdf9129;amazon_78b77593-59d2-42fd-8597-00b050dbda21;generic_51152983500988087;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
