Bombslinger;Bombslinger;Bombslinger;;videos\Bombslinger (2018).mp4;OK;images\Bombslinger (2018).webp;;Amazon;Mode4;Plug In Digital;11/04/2018;"A Bomberman-inspired Wild West action game with bombs! A solo hardcore reinvention of the iconic explosive action!

Wear the poncho of the Bombslinger, a ruthless bandit turned peaceful rancher on a quest to avenge the murder of his missus and destruction of his ranch at the hands of his former posse. Bomb your way through hordes of enemies and master the classic bomb-slinging gameplay in a solo adventure with procedurally generated levels, character progression with skill upgrades, and a variety of offensive and defensive items. And when you want a break from the solo adventure, take the fight to your friends in hectic 4-player deathmatch battles!";Adventure, Strategy, Indie, Shooter, Arcade, Fighting, Card & Board Game;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/475960/157473/1425a5a7c39ec38beae69b73b0694ffc468512ae/1751290918/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1523454894;amazon_88046aa6-0e4d-4f5f-b48c-37de955cc815;steam_475960;xboxone_912892717;test_bombslinger;amazon_88046aa6-0e4d-4f5f-b48c-37de955cc815;twitch_88046aa6-0e4d-4f5f-b48c-37de955cc815;test_abbf0dcc7e908c9e3711b1d53427ea82500e3333;test_1c87a0674cc3a60ffa7a726fbd5763a92add20a4;test_0f909f34a348feda2fdabff54b46dd98512a8ff1;test_6193fe64eabfc82c710063441761efc410268a5b;test_34bf12-bombslinger;amazon_dabce729-a8b5-cb0b-9820-bf19434aca35;generic_51141835655516419;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Indiana Jones and the Fate of Atlantis;Indiana Jones and the Fate of Atlantis;Indiana Jones and the Fate of Atlantis;;videos\Indiana Jones and the Fate of Atlantis (1992).mp4;OK;images\Indiana Jones and the Fate of Atlantis (1992).webp;;Amazon;LucasArts;Disney Interactive, U.S. Gold, LucasArts;01/06/1992;"A point-and-click adventure game by LucasArts originally released in 1992. Almost a year later, it was reissued on CD-ROM as an enhanced ""talkie"" edition with full voice acting and digitized sound effects. In 2009, this version was also released as an unlockable extra of the Wii action game Indiana Jones and the Staff of Kings, and as a digitally distributed Steam title. The seventh game to use the script language SCUMM, Fate of Atlantis has the player explore environments and interact with objects and characters by using commands constructed with predetermined verbs. It features three unique paths to select, influencing story development, gameplay and puzzles.";Adventure, Puzzle, Point-and-click;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/6010/96899/c9985a75cec4da9dd35d501d7c11b9c22cce70d1/1751245948/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1491238597;amazon_88612dcd-7348-4588-89eb-ef41d873de11;steam_6010;gog_1207666293;humble_indianajones_andthefateofatlantis_trove;discord_492162663976140810;egg_atlantis;gameuk_atlantis;amiga_atlantis;test_184;amiga_atlantis-steam;amiga_atlantis-1;amiga_atlantis-fm;amiga_atlantis-it;amiga_atlantis-mac;amiga_atlantis-amiga;test_6010;amiga_atlantis-fm-1;c64_24477471477653;test_a20ca5dfadfea28f540ce1321866362f029ea18e;test_3133116349144521;test_0a5a77ea5f14e5da261a2c880ac7f73e70cfdedc;jaguar_1529840668565;amiga_atlantis-steam-win;amazon_88612dcd-7348-4588-89eb-ef41d873de11;twitch_88612dcd-7348-4588-89eb-ef41d873de11;test_2c667a1f84356a028813ff15fff65ba54c96fcd3;test_7fa2b22f054b1486a5ba0d959f837caa551738e2;amiga_atlantis-de;dotemu_20843c68c446f43c689c46460a1ef898bf54c741;amiga_atlantis-fr;test_17bd7631100c0c7b09f8f26ce44032209f8112f6;jaguar