The Abandoned Planet;The Abandoned Planet;The Abandoned Planet;;videos\The Abandoned Planet (2024).mp4;OK;images\The Abandoned Planet (2024).webp;;Amazon;Dexter Team Games;Snapbreak;29/08/2024;When a wormhole tears open in space, an astronaut is hurled down and crashes on a distant planet. But where is she? Where are all the inhabitants of the planet? And how is she going to get back home? Solve the puzzle and piece together the mystery in this 2D, pixel art, first person, point and click adventure.;Adventure, Indie, Puzzle, Point-and-click;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/2014470/535803/93b93665790bb2ce0b08d0133e73f6a80aa46474/1751067578/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1713817395;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.03e49736-1880-4850-a59f-012b70e7dc96;steam_2014470;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.03e49736-1880-4850-a59f-012b70e7dc96;humble_theabandonedplanet_bundle_steam;xboxone_1757050834;generic_55521797526020422;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Star Wars Rogue Squadron;Star Wars: Rogue Squadron;Star Wars Rogue Squadron;;videos\Star Wars Rogue Squadron (1998).mp4;OK;images\Star Wars Rogue Squadron (1998).webp;;Amazon;LucasArts, Factor 5;Nintendo, LucasArts, Disney Interactive Studios, Gradiente;17/11/1998;"It is a time of great rejoicing in the galaxy. Luke Skywalker, with the help of Wedge Antilles, has blown up the Death Star. But there is little time to celebrate. The mighty Empire is gathering strength for a determined, all-out assault on the Rebel forces.

To save the Rebel Alliance from this Imperial onslaught, Luke Skywalker and Wedge Antilles have assembled the Rogue Squadron, a group of twelve of the most skilled battle-tested starfighter pilots. You will fly into battle as Luke Skywalker, to engage in intense, fast-paced planetary air-to-ground and air-to-air missions ‒ dogfights, search and destroy, reconnaissance, bombing runs, rescue assignments, and more.";Shooter;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/455910/55173/4546ec547bcfef7a5df13cdaeb71c1a3fabf314d/1750532706/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1462237367;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.054a8a9a-075f-4b2e-9ff6-113f743226c3;steam_455910;gog_1421404950;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0003166;n64_83C225CC;humble_star_warstm_rogue_squadron_3d_steam;n64_A6E336CE;n64_65A8FBA0;n64_4A479574;n64_C88E5638;n64_2D6FA165;n64_6289645F;n64_Star Wars: Rogue Squadron;n64_Star Wars - Rogue Squadron;n64_13CC4CA4;n64_Star Wars - Shutsugeki! Rogue Chuutai;test_1fcd0f0a92d17ea0df6bd411cd6ed500b1a2fc97;test_20e2651a82049fc5c13ccecce57b6b50692affa3;test_ac95182a819c1b89b8ee70e3843df2acefeb81d2;n64_ac95182a819c1b89b8ee70e3843df2acefeb81d2;test_5aa2d566554bd6d99388420c52f0bb3296e45dc0;test_95c4fe32294a488ba4d73a3026b6c9068e420cd3;test_25a6a72a2c10f8c1c5c6cca46881e9e269413270;test_a5036c0b3379eaad9372fd881fa551bba3cf4001;test_caefa52ee27a3e608b0cef87716d1a87faeae8b1;test_c12e1c6fb47a67da463c50b705ec682ec24ae80d;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0003166@subscription;ncube_Star Wars - Rogue Squadron;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.054a8a9a-075f-4b2e-9ff6-113f743226c3;test_d7d44fe1e3d1b3b25d7f339dd8e869584761b991;test_b624bc3b142178365647f3a6e395da7ffb52c653;twitch_amzn1.adg.product.054a8a9a-075f-4b2e-9ff6-113f743226c3;generic_51154260230104995;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
