King of the Monsters 2;King of the Monsters 2;King of the Monsters 2;;;OK;images\King of the Monsters 2 (1992).webp;;Amazon;SNK;SNK, Takara;19/01/1992;Alien super monsters have returned and are trying to invade Earth again! Now, Super Geon, Atomic Guy, and Cyber Woo must fight to retain control of the planet. Each one has special attacks and powers. Take on monsters that have unique abilities never seen before, including fire breath, aerial spins, and radioactive blasts. Challenge a friend, or have him help you out in the two-player option. Battle your way through seven levels of intense action in King of The Monsters 2.;Fighting;;;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.42316c09-6463-4624-97fa-e338a5f0cd20;snes_King of the Monsters 2;snes_1327;snes_369106782;snes_47245673515;snes_0B677A37;segag_King of the Monsters 2;segag_369106782;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.42316c09-6463-4624-97fa-e338a5f0cd20;test_9beebee78649cea485df39e4d1873bffde046e54;test_15579a3862b3686d13644d61c0449ac85b08f6ee;gog_1867335796;twitch_amzn1.adg.product.42316c09-6463-4624-97fa-e338a5f0cd20;generic_51153181240843972;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Aces of the Luftwaffe - Squadron Extended Edition;Aces of the Luftwaffe - Squadron Extended Edition;Aces of the Luftwaffe - Squadron Extended Edition;;;OK;images\Aces of the Luftwaffe - Squadron Extended Edition (2019).webp;;Amazon;HandyGames;HandyGames;26/02/2019;"Aces of the Luftwaffe - Squadron is an action-packed, vertically scrolling shoot ‘em up. 
Dodge bullets, collect massive power ups and wisely use special abilities as you defeat waves of enemies. Upgrade each member of your squadron with their personal skill tree as you level up. 
You can take on the Aces with up to 3 friends in an epic 4 player local co-op battle. 
Includes the Nebelgeschwader DLC, effectively doubling the size of the original game.";Shooter;;;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.42611da8-7064-4bf0-83a7-9147add5b6d9;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.42611da8-7064-4bf0-83a7-9147add5b6d9;test_27af11eac86dc68b1e6bd7ed727e9ae6e85df432;generic_52305080459127865;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
