Icewind Dale Enhanced Edition;Icewind Dale: Enhanced Edition;Icewind Dale Enhanced Edition;;videos\Icewind Dale Enhanced Edition (2014).mp4;OK;images\Icewind Dale Enhanced Edition (2014).webp;;Amazon;Overhaul Games;Beamdog;30/10/2014;"Originally released in 2000, Icewind Dale is a Dungeons & Dragons game set in Wizards of The Coast's legendary Forgotten Realms. This Enhanced Edition allows players to experience the epic adventure on PC, Mac, Linux, iPad, iPhone, and Android tablets and phones, and includes a host of new features:

• Swords and Sorcery: Discover dozens of new spells and items, including new magic armor and weapons.
• Blackguards and Wizard Slayers: Select from over 30 new kits and classes to create the perfect adventuring party.
• Bring A Friend: Join your fellow adventurers in cooperative, cross-platform multiplayer games.
• See The Unseen: Explore quest content cut from the original game, now finished and restored.
• More to Experience: Icewind Dale: Enhanced Edition includes both the Heart of Winter and Trials of the Luremaster expansion packs.";Role-playing (RPG), Adventure, Strategy;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/321800/26872/ea8d5f59c10d2e5babd76e452b5e5fba8be15ee5/1750507640/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1447364560;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.484268fa-d1e7-4754-ad8d-a5181f12f8b0;steam_321800;gog_1207666683;test_/icewind-dale-enhanced-edition-free-download/;test_icewind-dale-enhanced-edition;playfire_icewind-dale-enhanced-edition;epic_7d2ed6b13ab94a0b83a8f39199fe5b9d;fanatical_icewind-dale-enhanced-edition;humble_icewinddale_enhancededition_bundle_steam;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.484268fa-d1e7-4754-ad8d-a5181f12f8b0;test_570377b74fc536becd2b7c4391ecd6fb99cdc142;test_6c24db8f4c7f9efd7f17779b7a8db08a3de5c194;test_97710aa1d9e16c11db737303a668b9aebceda464;humble_icewinddale_enhancededition_row_bundle_steam;twitch_amzn1.adg.product.484268fa-d1e7-4754-ad8d-a5181f12f8b0;humble_icewinddale_enhancededition_sea_bundle_steam;humble_icewinddale_enhancededition_latam_bundle_steam;test_02c13ae0cdc4f25696771d8609ee2f7f4923d027;epic_60b86a02acd64f21bf37942e81ad27d2;generic_51152993758783632;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Trinity Fusion;Trinity Fusion;Trinity Fusion;;videos\Trinity Fusion (2023).mp4;OK;images\Trinity Fusion (2023).webp;;Amazon;Angry Mob Games;Angry Mob Games;15/12/2023;"Take control of your parallel selves on a mission to save the dying multiverse in this rogue-lite action platformer! Explore dark, sci-fi worlds and engage in fast-paced, smooth and precise combat.

The various branches of the multiverse are always changing. Fight through a combination of procedurally-generated levels as well as hand-crafted challenges and arenas that will put your skills to the test. Levels with 3D graphics are seamlessly constructed out of hundreds of hand-made rooms.

With weapons and attack systems that leverage our previous experience working on fighting games. You’ll slide, dash and dodge between enemy attacks and strike back with an arsenal of satisfying special weapons and abilities.

Each of your parallel selves has their own world with multiple biomes to explore, as well as their own sets of unique abilities and weapons. Travel through a universe of desolate wastes and caverns roamed by mutant creatures, escape the endless forges and labs of a world ruled by machines, and survive the dangerous sky cities of a post-human society.";Role-playing (RPG), Indie, Platform, Fighting;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/1911360/629223/71927bb1251b58de2a2a633b10045bf6908f88aa/1751494666/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1699903462;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.49c149a1-6efb-4c80-9bd0-20f49518da23;steam_1911360;steam_2230600;xboxone_1902947501;epic_37406adc84e9498d81eb3aa8fae07351;xboxone_2028002991;xboxone_1800716708;gog_2090070295;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.49c149a1-6efb-4c80-9bd0-20f49518da23;humble_trinityfusion_bundle_steam;generic_55831005718763932;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
