Super Sidekicks;Super Sidekicks;Super Sidekicks;;;OK;images\Super Sidekicks (1992).webp;;Amazon;SNK;SNK, SNK Playmore;14/12/1992;"Published in 1993, the original Super Sidekicks (known as Tokuten Ou, ""Goal-Scoring King"" in Japan) was SNK's first soccer video game. It features 12 teams divided into two groups which compete for the ""SNK Cup"" (the main differences between teams is their formations on the field):

Group A: Germany, Italy, Spain, England, Mexico, Japan
Group B: Argentina, Holland, Brazil, France, United States, South Korea

The players' team plays against all the others in their group, then it goes into an elimination tournament's semifinals and then the final to win the cup. There was also a hidden feature in the game, which wasn't documented, and affects a single player game. During a free kick for the CPU if the player has tapped button A for player two, the CPU performs a short-shot, while pressing the button A performs a longer kick.";Sport, Arcade;;;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.5752cc6f-88c1-4e96-9a1c-04eaedb34ddf;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.5752cc6f-88c1-4e96-9a1c-04eaedb34ddf;test_27c8e40b79106f5c3ec4555cc70179aeed31f7a0;test_098e1ccffdbc7da4849d3e0cf0bca71d21547c81;gog_1410950050;twitch_amzn1.adg.product.5752cc6f-88c1-4e96-9a1c-04eaedb34ddf;test_f8a1da7f2bdf5e694a2617d07e538ac37cc944ec;generic_51154295654727654;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Ninja Commando;Ninja Commando;Ninja Commando;;;OK;images\Ninja Commando (1992).webp;;Amazon;Alpha Denshi;D4 Enterprise, SNK, Alpha Denshi;29/01/1992;"Ninja Commando is a vertically scrolling action game released by ADK in 1992. Players choose from among three ninjas - Joe, descended from the Koga ninja; Rayar, a woman who has learned the ways of the Iga ninja; and Ryu, descendant of the famous ninja Fuma Kotaro - as they pursue the merchant of death known as Spider, who plans to use a time machine to bring havoc to the world. The battle spans seven time periods, including the Stone Age, the Egyptian era and the Japanese Civil War era.";Platform, Shooter, Arcade, Fighting;;;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.588ce979-f6b0-44cc-9ff3-7ce8905c3f64;ncube_Ninja Commando;neo_Ninja Commando;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.588ce979-f6b0-44cc-9ff3-7ce8905c3f64;test_daafc1af8a1a0660abce66154a0bfb6af0eab44f;test_88b2ae23a70005bbad508d5ceeef5b79890936f7;gog_1951064059;twitch_amzn1.adg.product.588ce979-f6b0-44cc-9ff3-7ce8905c3f64;3do_Ninja Commando;generic_51153346586903275;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
In Other Waters;In Other Waters;In Other Waters;;videos\In Other Waters (2020).mp4;OK;images\In Other Waters (2020).webp;;Amazon;Jump Over the Age;Fellow Traveller;03/04/2020;"In a future where humanity's ceaseless consumption has expanded out to encompass the stars, and Earth's last biological life clings to a poisoned planet, In Other Waters tells the story of Ellery Vas, a biologist who stumbles upon extraterrestrial life.

When a routine exoplanet study goes wrong, and her partner Minae Nomura disappears into an alien ocean, Ellery is left with little more than an antiquated diving suit and a strange AI to guide her.

Together they will trace Nomura, and in turn, discover impossible life, journey this alien ocean and dredge up secrets that were meant to be lost forever, beneath these turquoise waves.";Adventure, Indie, Puzzle, Simulator;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/890720/275879/ddd7f94a084f5b3e4c604e45dd6388e0b6cae6c9/1750594012/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1686299930;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.5a2dea57-7759-4312-8cd4-986ac1c46a45;steam_890720;itch_214835;gog_1221608838;humble_inotherwaters_storefront_steam_Pkt1E;nswitch_0100B6E01056E000;test_/in-other-waters-free-download/;test_in-other-waters;humble_inotherwaters;humble_inotherwaters_choice_steam;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.5a2dea57-7759-4312-8cd4-986ac1c46a45;test_af3db30a29ffee7d2a171e1bf29ec10d553a7349;twitch_amzn1.adg.product.5a2dea57-7759-4312-8cd4-986ac1c46a45;epic_198bfd99445544769e7114a6bb84b95e;humble_inotherwaters_bundle_steam;generic_51152998656622770;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Mutation Nation;Mutation Nation;Mutation Nation;;;OK;images\Mutation Nation (1992).webp;;Amazon;SNK;SNK;16/01/1992;"The Slum... an area of town completely forgotten. No one could imagine the cruelness suffered by innocent people who were transformed into horrible mutant creatures by genetic experiments. They hovered everywhere and completely took control of the town.

