Dive in and discover ancient truths with these twenty new quests.";Role-playing (RPG), Strategy, Turn-based strategy (TBS), Indie;;;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.6d93b0e4-54dd-4046-9363-d72d877ef6fd;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.6d93b0e4-54dd-4046-9363-d72d877ef6fd;humble_endlesslegend_definitiveedition_storefront_steam_VSsgo;humble_endlesslegend_definitiveedition_storefront_steam_wdINf;humble_endlesslegend_definitiveedition_storefront_steam_ZdaVv;humble_endlesslegend_definitiveedition_storefront_steam_6Y2Py;humble_endlesslegend_definitiveedition_storefront_steam_wo7Ik;generic_58643452009418578;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
