Fahrenheit Indigo Prophecy Remastered;Fahrenheit: Indigo Prophecy Remastered;Fahrenheit Indigo Prophecy Remastered;;videos\Fahrenheit Indigo Prophecy Remastered (2015).mp4;OK;images\Fahrenheit Indigo Prophecy Remastered (2015).webp;;Amazon;Quantic Dream;Aspyr Media, Quantic Dream;28/01/2015;"Guilt is a Chilling Feeling... 
 
Originally released in 2005, Fahrenheit (known as Indigo Prophecy in North America) was a breakthrough in interactive narrative, teetering between the worlds of cinema and gaming while also embracing them, carving its own unique genre in the entertainment landscape. This newly remastered edition features updated graphics, controller support AND is based on the uncut/uncensored international version of the game. 
 
With a rich multilayered narrative, innovative presentation, and a chilling musical score by famed Hollywood composer Angelo Badalementi, Fahrenheit: Indigo Prophecy Remastered serves as the definitive version of the supernatural murder mystery and (re)introduces the groundbreaking title to old and new fans alike.";Role-playing (RPG), Adventure;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/312840/30388/fa63bf2c042a3d7cc02f60565f8cbb1bb0daa14c/1750506621/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1447368037;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.6ed13be7-1d52-42b0-af03-9f487492ae93;steam_312840;steam_9740;psn_CUSA04798_00;humble_fahrenheit_indigoprophecy_steam;humble_fahrenheit_indigoprophecy_yogscast2018_steam;humble_fahrenheit_indigoprophecy_conquercovid19_steam;ps2_2494;ps2_Indigo Prophecy;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.6ed13be7-1d52-42b0-af03-9f487492ae93;test_73b293aec531e167205a55eecd3c68b750845a6f;twitch_amzn1.adg.product.6ed13be7-1d52-42b0-af03-9f487492ae93;gog_1146026335;test_2b6d6b1f4e0842e5e939a0ed80ec84ebd3113a6d;humble_fahrenheit_indigoprophecyremastered_row_steam;generic_51152848967914856;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
