Planescape Torment Enhanced Edition;Planescape Torment: Enhanced Edition;Planescape Torment Enhanced Edition;;videos\Planescape Torment Enhanced Edition (2017).mp4;OK;images\Planescape Torment Enhanced Edition (2017).webp;;Amazon;Beamdog;Beamdog;11/04/2017;"""Discover an incredibly rich story and a unique setting unlike anything else in fantasy. Defeat strange and alien creatures, engage in rich dialogue, and explore the dark and dangerous Planescape setting in this 50+ hour RPG classic.

Millions of Planescape: Torment fans have enjoyed the strange and dangerous city of Sigil and surrounding planes through the Nameless One's eyes. Now it’s your turn. This is Planescape: Torment like you’ve never seen before.

Enhanced Edition - Key Features:
- Enhanced Planescape: Chris Avellone, Lead Designer on Planescape Torment, has partnered with Beamdog to curate gameplay updates, bug fixes, and enhancements to best capture his original vision for the game.

- Remastered Music: The full Planescape: Torment soundtrack has been remastered in-game to add more depth to Sigil and the multiverse.

- 4K Interface: Sigil has never looked this good! The interface of Planescape: Torment has been rebuilt in high definition with tons of new convenience features.

- A Planescape For Today: The Enhanced Edition includes modern features such as tab highlighting, area zooming, combat log, quickloot, and more!""";Role-playing (RPG), Adventure, Strategy;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/466300/95180/4e6d52cb046db9da0c46941c951fafb6a6a1fa53/1750534406/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1490733888;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.93c268bc-c898-4e7c-b866-ea9c93c781b0;steam_466300;gog_1132393016;beamdog_4cc533fe-aa50-4b0b-bc5c-ad196fe361df;minecraft_4cc533fe-aa50-4b0b-bc5c-ad196fe361df;minecraft_a697fbc9-912a-44e1-bbca-738ae2691735;minecraft_921fecaf-5529-4f06-9bd5-3f698314eeee;test_/planescape-torment-enhanced-edition-free-download/;test_planescape-torment-enhanced-edition;fanatical_planescape-torment-enhanced-edition;epic_b0cc370c45d34e47a39b056867b61388;humble_planescape_torment_enhancededition_steam;humble_planescape_tormentenhancededition_bundle_steam;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.93c268bc-c898-4e7c-b866-ea9c93c781b0;humble_planescape_torment_enhancededition_row_bundle_steam;twitch_amzn1.adg.product.93c268bc-c898-4e7c-b866-ea9c93c781b0;humble_planescape_torment_enhancededition_sea_bundle_steam;humble_planescape_torment_enhancededition_latam_bundle_steam;epic_813bce1ade924597993b6d4b4e3cd288;generic_51153495929584996;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
