The Stillness of the Wind;The Stillness of the Wind;The Stillness of the Wind;;videos\The Stillness of the Wind (2019).mp4;OK;images\The Stillness of the Wind (2019).webp;;Amazon;Memory of God;Fellow Traveller;30/01/2019;"One by one, everyone left the once bustling village for the city. Everyone, except Talma. Now approaching the end of her days, she maintains a simple, solitary way of life, surviving, subsisting, tending to her homestead and her goats.

Develop your own personal routine as you care for your farm and your animals. Tend to your goats, make cheese with their milk, collect eggs and cook meals, grow vegetables and barter with the travelling merchant who brings increasingly disturbing letters from your family in the city.

A follow up to the critically acclaimed Where the Goats Are, The Stillness of the Wind is a quiet rumination on life and loss.";Adventure, Indie, Simulator;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/828900/206769/f5b6f6ec806bd6655dbc483e37dd5eae73b1dd28/1750587446/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1548776730;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.a10b8ae4-785f-4aa9-bf60-844d9d0b5a25;steam_828900;xboxone_1680770844;itch_287843;winstore_9pfd15g4w9rz;humble_thestillnessofthewind_australiafirerelief_bundle_steam;humble_thestillnessofthewind;humble_thestillnessofthewind_choice_steam;itch_the-stillness-of-the-wind;test_287843;test_/the-stillness-of-the-wind-free-download/;test_the-stillness-of-the-wind;humble_thestillnessofthewind_steam;gog_1533394584;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.a10b8ae4-785f-4aa9-bf60-844d9d0b5a25;test_514d4845d00ad6d47a4952c348b39d711bd4b30c;test_7443dfb5a13e9f509a1a751cd93a5d526116d215;test_828900;twitch_amzn1.adg.product.a10b8ae4-785f-4aa9-bf60-844d9d0b5a25;humble_stillnessofthewind_bundle_steam;generic_51295404140117895;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Soccer Brawl;Soccer Brawl;Soccer Brawl;;;OK;images\Soccer Brawl (1992).webp;;Amazon;SNK;SNK;13/01/1992;The Cybernetic players use special kick shots and built-in arm phasers to destroy other players. Make sure your power meter is FULL when exercising these brutal tactics. Both stadiums, which are magnetically enclosed, enable you to kick or pass... off the wall! There are no fouls in this league, so watch your back or you'll get pulverized by the opposing team! You'll find here the most advanced sport in the world of soccer... SOCCER BRAWL!;Sport, Arcade, Fighting;;;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.a1d15fb4-f3d0-4372-a917-5a95a9aa7dbf;nwii_EB3J;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.a1d15fb4-f3d0-4372-a917-5a95a9aa7dbf;test_0b5a9a6abd9ff95e32e94f30cacaf69ac3e2c145;test_8167e8d94836da9a26bd557b6a000fdabf3af652;gog_1097533180;twitch_amzn1.adg.product.a1d15fb4-f3d0-4372-a917-5a95a9aa7dbf;generic_51154219583350081;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Faraway 2 Jungle Escape;Faraway 2: Jungle Escape;Faraway 2 Jungle Escape;;;OK;images\Faraway 2 Jungle Escape (2018).webp;;Amazon;Pine Studio;;01/05/2018;"Escape all new temples in Faraway 2: Jungle Escape that are full of new challenges and mysterious puzzles. This room escape game will surely challenge your puzzle escaping ability. Sequel to one of the best escape games ever with over a million players! A room escape puzzle game that will completely challenge your mind, captivate you & offer hours of amazing mobile gaming entertainment.

COMPLEX PUZZLES
Explore 18 new temples packed with escape puzzles, Explore a 3D world that will captivate you from the moment you begin. Turn, look and explore mind-bending puzzles and contraptions.

IMMERSIVE WORLD
Relax to the ambient soundtrack and the easy to navigate the 3D world that you will find in an escape game, with an abundance of secrets to discover.

THE MYSTERY CONTINUES
You have many more pages of your father’s missing journal to find, maybe then you will unlock your family’s past. This is an escape game that will keep you engaged for many hours!

NEW FEATURES
In game camera allows you to take snapshots and save them for later use.

TRY FOR FREE
Enjoy 9 free escape levels before you decide to purchase the remaining levels and experience the whole Faraway 2: Jungle Escape story that will leave you impressed.

SUPER WIDESCREEN SUPPORT
The puzzle game looks beautiful on new 18:9 phones and also shines on tablet devices. Enjoy stunning and astoundingly detailed graphics that look exquisite.

SUPPORTS IPHONE X SCREEN
Compatible with new standard screen sizes for iPhone X.

