Two Point Hospital;Two Point Hospital;Two Point Hospital;;videos\Two Point Hospital (2018).mp4;OK;images\Two Point Hospital (2018).webp;;Amazon, Epic Games Store;Two Point Studios;Sega;29/08/2018;"Design stunning hospitals, cure peculiar illnesses and manage troublesome staff as you spread your budding healthcare organisation across Two Point County. 
 
Design Your Hospital 
Build and customise your hospital - it is yours after all - with specialist diagnosis and treatment facilities, as well as the very latest in ornamental technology! 
 
Cure Your Patients 
Feeling light-headed? Just wait until you see the other unusual illnesses afflicting the people of Two Point County. Care for, and profit from, the ill: that seems like it’s probably a win-win. They’ll need feeding, entertaining and curing if they’re going to recommend you to all their equally unwell friends! That cash isn’t going to make itself, now. 
 
Manage Your Staff 
Hire your staff, juggle their demands and cater to their personalities. Train a crack team that can handle every sickly challenge that’s thrown at it, and fire anyone that can’t. 
 
Expand Your Organisation 
Grow the sickness business across the beautiful Two Point County. Research illnesses and develop new inventions to compete with rival healthcare companies. 
 
Collaborate and Compete with Friends 
Once you’ve conquered the world with your medical empire, contribute to Two Point County’s global medical community with collaborative research projects, or demonstrate your medical prowess in competitive multiplayer challenges.";Strategy, Indie, Simulator;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/535930/181784/94f65733a5abb3866ac6418ebd50eff834616abb/1750547367/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1535609052;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.d14f6257-7fa1-4887-a09a-666a6f051a6f, epic_4ad17ed617f44a4dbf7e8a960484c619;steam_535930;xboxone_2050010864;humble_twopointhospital_eu_steam;humble_twopointhospital_row_steam;humble_twopointhospital_rucis_steam;humble_twopointhospital_monthly_steam;humble_twopointhospital_preorder_eu_steam;xboxone_1692546142;psn_CUSA15884_00;psn_CUSA16081_00;humble_twopointhospital_preorder_row_steam;humble_twopointhospital_tr_steam;winstore_9n08s5vpc4sx;itch_9d23bdad22e8c991eec1c40aaa5b8f10b1f86dde315604587bf124f6;itch_XFxSYWlkc2VydmVyXGdcTXkgRHJpdmVcRml0R2lybCBHYW1lc1xUd28gUG9pbnQgSG9zcGl0YWwgW0ZpdEdpcmwgUmVwYWNrXQ==;origin_e86bf29460fc74f7c647ba0ab2d2e842a5f39a6e;origin_8eb09a87eb29cfa202414f88b2e2dba53ab79570b69c42b16709efed36fe4607;humble_twopointhospital;test_291a1f52a6979958982b2b7c8db5e6511588661b;test_5139eb4119788930ef667b6df5d7f43600f55ada;test_a582443c46b17857374139a0405dcf85109f57a5;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0004243;humble_twopointhospital_sa_steam;test_/two-point-hospital-free-download/;test_two-point-hospital;playfire_two-point-hospital;nswitch_010031200E044000;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0004243@subscription;test_steam_twopointhospital;test_gfn_535930;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.d14f6257-7fa1-4887-a09a-666a6f051a6f;test_2a0edda0e5ab9ad8cdd1eaaee3dc6d4fed1de873;twitch_amzn1.adg.product.d14f6257-7fa1-4887-a09a-666a6f051a6f;gog_1940028140;test_gfn_100234411;test_CUSA15884_00;test_b4ba4c229cae8d516548c288d2fe395d3799e17a;test_480319d0bddb09f3fee1fa31e508d2257c9a6721;test_4ff5afc0a90e0d4253b919688e7d4f0a574b0c4d;test_535930;test_8d6db5fed3a1c879b82f7715905597e8