Bang Bang Racing;Bang Bang Racing;Bang Bang Racing;;videos\Bang Bang Racing (2011).mp4;OK;images\Bang Bang Racing (2011).webp;;Amazon;Kalypso Media Digital;Digital Reality Software & Playbox;13/05/2011;"Bang Bang Racing is a distinct arcade game focusing not only on the speed but also on the technical driving skills. The very intuitive control system and the exciting tracks provide endless fun for everyone in the family.

Bang Bang Racing delivers fast-paced racing around every corner and down every straight. Drive high-speed, pumped-up racing cars through cones, tires and exploding barrels! Be one step ahead of your competitors, finding shortcuts, repairing your car in the pit lane, and dominating your opponents from the top-down view.";Arcade, Racing;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/207020/7865/0c1a04938d7fe82024b07452c4b27da7b5e98777/1751246492/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1447355981;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.e13c50c9-d548-4e6f-a85a-7f70308279e8;steam_207020;humble_bangbangracing_steam;psx_Bang Bang Racing;psn_NPUB30616_00;fanatical_bang-bang-racing;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.e13c50c9-d548-4e6f-a85a-7f70308279e8;test_7cf549914c52b654a655405907ab2c6fee1e9149;test_ab77587e102ce02b0bf1f57c036c1e59f0051561;twitch_amzn1.adg.product.e13c50c9-d548-4e6f-a85a-7f70308279e8;test_a363285621b8a568b349de46470c66b782ec8402;generic_51141467829869243;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Last Resort;Last Resort;Last Resort;;;OK;images\Last Resort (2021).webp;;Amazon;;;28/06/2021;Last Resort is a small co-op shooter in which you and up to 3 others defend humanity's first hotel on Mars against hostile aliens. Defend & power up generators, upgrade your weapons and gun down hordes of aliens to save the hotel!;Arcade;;;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.e159b43d-77c7-4f22-8b1f-dd00f827f93e;atari_Last Resort;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.e159b43d-77c7-4f22-8b1f-dd00f827f93e;test_54ae38a8ccdbd1b5044718f5d23b9e3967baa748;test_b87c327e9e40cd39c61e88513639a449990ee370;generic_54771837208214236;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
The Forgotten City;The Forgotten City;The Forgotten City;;videos\The Forgotten City (2021).mp4;OK;images\The Forgotten City (2021).webp;;Amazon;Modern Storyteller;Plug In Digital, Dear Villagers;28/07/2021;"The Forgotten City is a time travel murder mystery set in a mythological city.

Deep underground in an ancient Roman city, twenty-six trapped explorers lay dead because one of them broke a mysterious law. Within, a portal leads back into the past, allowing you to change their fate – or witness their deaths in a time loop for eternity.

Fortunately, hope remains. The Forgotten City offers incredible freedom, inviting you to manipulate the timeline, Groundhog Day-style, so events play out differently. By talking with diverse characters, making tough choices in moral dilemmas, and thinking laterally, you can unlock vastly different endings.

The Forgotten City is a game about the human condition, for adults who enjoy figuring things out for themselves.";Role-playing (RPG), Adventure, Indie;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/874260/397630/ad1ed9197735f24a87996e17b4ad40f7424a5c97/1750592367/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1630422065;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.e31e4571-b8d9-444e-852f-93846749eb40;steam_874260;gog_1231956919;xboxone_1771770355;epic_ef063f88bc514433ae28420fb9030ca9;humble_theforgottencity_storefront_steam_34VRD;psn_CUSA26944_00;psn_PPSA03026_00;psn_CUSA26945_00;psn_PPSA03134_00;psn_PPSA03580_00;test_FitGirl12;psn_CUSA27773_00;humble_theforgottencity;humble_theforgottencity_row_choice_steam;humble_theforgottencity_cn_choice_steam;humble_theforgottencity_rucis_choice_steam;humble_theforgottencity_latam_choice_steam;humble_forgottencity_bundle_steam;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.e31e4571-b8d9-444e-852f-93846749eb40;test_bf66a71645fb5ce4e45cdd71e35db7c743efede8;generic_51296538417232046;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Zak McKracken and the Alien Mindbenders;Zak McKracken and the Alien Mindbenders;Zak McKracken and the Alien Mindbenders;;videos\Zak McKracken and the Alien Mindbenders (1988).mp4;OK;images\Zak McKracken and the Alien Mindbenders (1988).webp;;Amazon;Lucasfilm Games;Lucasfilm Games, Fujitsu Interactive;01/10/1988;"Zak McKracken is a tabloid reporter (and not a very good one at that). After having a psychedelic dream one day, Zak realizes that something is wrong -- space aliens are dumbifying the general public through the telephone system. Zak must stop this, but he can't do it alone. After finding a strange crystal, Zak manages to get the help of the anthropologist Annie and her friends, Melissa and Leslie. The four unlikely heroes must now figure out a way to destroy the dumbifying devices and save the Earth.

Zak McKracken and the Alien Mindbenders is a third-person puzzle-solving adventure similar in gameplay to Lucasfilm's breakthrough title Maniac Mansion. The player chooses verb commands (Open, Pick Up, Give, etc.; there are no Look or Talk commands) to interact with the game world. The game features up to four controllable protagonists; it is possible to switch between them at any time after they have been introduced, and also exchange inventory items if the characters are in the same location. The game can be described as a ""globe-trotting"" adventure, since the heroes are required to travel to different exotic countries and even leave the Earth for a while in order to complete it. Some of the puzzles are optional or can be solved in different ways.

The FM Towns version has VGA graphics with 256 colors and higher-quality music and sound effects.";Adventure, Point-and-click;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/559070/194835/8a4fb43d8a97a790de9786a4d32c98676b4fd951/1751301835/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1542411116;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.e3b3a12f-d30d-44eb-8b43-548081dc69fb;gog_1425040088;steam_559070;egg_zak-fm;egg_zak-v2;gameuk_zak-fm;gameuk_zak-v2;amiga_zak-fm;amiga_zak-v2;amiga_zak-v1-c64;amiga_zak-v2-de;amiga_zak;amiga_zak-v2-it;amiga_zak-v1;amiga_zak-v2-st;amiga_zak-v2-amiga;amiga_zak-fm-1;test_9ef6d4715dcf5daba5ef51cbe25773ac3d644f07;test_1f7e4f8f0f764be11e02a134789a036f70c875fb;test_f88fd1192dfeda1f9ac69894667aeab329ba3c8c;c64_1f7e4f8f0f764be11e02a134789a036f70c875fb;c64_9ef6d4715dcf5daba5ef51cbe25773ac3d644f07;c64_f88fd1192dfeda1f9ac69894667aeab329ba3c8c;c64_31195a6f12775767332de46d6098f1f68207d272;c64_f7345eb82b391a6e3ad2adfd585e2084ce1c0a27;c64_ea0f90d4b4bbe6119e8803cf31ca5ee8300cb3f4;test_5e71e151ee7e5e8dad19a0ec5050baa1dd79011c;test_de6bc2115649913265a9458f8988f30ba867a867;test_3a8d9fa63b68b9600ce383402d2c99bb8b93f466;test_6332744565790929;test_458d44109c93f338ef22b5de3e0ea169342e463a;test_1d58867a9715318cfe9f14be382ed731d62947fc;c64_146fbfff91b6f1dfc87e83d591626009a5c4655e;test_d80d69cee18783af5b86641288d0677eb7c2831c;c64_ed3af77b9911a40532281d7c35e242699439b0a6;test_25d91a749ec05f98775bfe044c649812f71381f5;c64_e35a2aa43713a75d806e0ec93e08a3cd1667778c;c64_5dd11ac43a0b9a740b78b110028b2d5f7865d67a;c64_a7c54504a55a276c607d2d4f59de00739c32099b;test_493391b38d71f3f051471c36c0cacb4643e73fa2;test_908034a8fe51b7eedb61ad813901cba7e4f4d1ec;test_27573042b99deeb3363dab7cbfc72ba99b1736e7;test_d419de19c6302747f6d853034f94d496f282fec6;c64_Zak Mckracken and the Alien Mindbenders;amiga_zak-v1-c64-de-1;amiga_zak-v1-c64-de;amiga_zak-v1-c64-de-2;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.e3b3a12f-d30d-44eb-8b43-548081dc69fb;test_158f4d4651c9966cc055815ab002a9fe3ed4867a;amiga_zak-fm-4;amiga_zak-fm-3
Liberated;Liberated;Liberated;;videos\Liberated (2020).mp4;OK;images\Liberated (2020).webp;;Amazon;Atomic Wolf;Walkabout Games;02/06/2020;Players will experience a story about a world where government authorities use advanced technology to manipulate the population. Civil rights are a thing of the past, with the government engaging in complete surveillance of every citizen in the world. Social media activity, online payments, and GPS location tracking from mobile devices are just some of the ways every single person is being monitored. In this world, there are insurgents resisting this oppression, fighting for their freedom, while government agents try to maintain order and control. In Liberated, players will experience both sides of this conflict, with every choice they make changing the course of the story.;Role-playing (RPG), Adventure, Indie, Platform, Visual Novel;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/875310/301841/fb0ad1166bd051f00af767f92c3ed1ebbc53d3d1/1751156963/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1600785090;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.e75a0723-ff30-4fb7-bc0c-edc573d99cd1;steam_875310;gog_1780442795;discord_6598648f-2d61-4aca-9016-f6cdd5a99e84;gog_1484808928;steam_1358880;test_/liberated-free-download/;test_liberated;humble_liberated_steam;fanatical_liberated;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.e75a0723-ff30-4fb7-bc0c-edc573d99cd1;twitch_amzn1.adg.product.e75a0723-ff30-4fb7-bc0c-edc573d99cd1;test_32b900afc63ff173a031e180d2d09f8326a0b600;test_946c47ae57f21e9949795532020664deb357644d;humble_liberated_standwithukraine_bundle_gog;psn_CUSA26979_00;test_62db4b7c19f3bb32308e0d9b5648b3439340176e;psn_CUSA26980_00;epic_f6f363ffe9bc467d890a589d287000aa;amazon_dcbe732e-857b-6bea-b293-22817917a195;generic_52138784841777754;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Etherborn;Etherborn;Etherborn;;videos\Etherborn (2019).mp4;OK;images\Etherborn (2019).webp;;Amazon;Altered Matter;Akupara Games;18/07/2019;"Etherborn is an environmental puzzle platformer built on exploring and understanding gravity-shifting structures.

You are a voiceless being that has just been born into a world where a bodiless voice calls to you, patiently awaiting your arrival. As your first thoughts emerge, you realise your journey has just begun. You must reach this ethereal voice to fully understand your own existence.";Adventure, Indie, Platform, Puzzle;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/812160/233771/9588b69534e1ede69c645bef9bedc8b2f29d4645/1751147714/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1563461827;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.e8de124d-8354-47ee-a388-e04739df05af;steam_812160;gog_1413035173;psn_CUSA15335_00;xboxone_1949522443;humble_etherborn_storefront_steam_AMHyX;psn_CUSA15516_00;humble_etherborn_choice_steam;humble_etherborn_trove;twitch_2a6974ca-e747-46e9-ba20-512ffbf343d3;amazon_2a6974ca-e747-46e9-ba20-512ffbf343d3;3ds_2a6974ca-e747-46e9-ba20-512ffbf343d3;test_77529;test_Etherborn;discord_0763b55b-d35f-4d82-9d5c-04da7f529c68;humble_etherborn;riot_45790;humble_etherborn_drm_free_Ir1S4;riot_riot-45790;test_/etherborn-free-download/;test_3b3994b6ed3be75fac0a131e0c65397acee6c8f9;test_65d93677668277dc80f61bb1d6fd66278d882869;test_1def7f4eb91d6c43c288e6f3d59c269892e5c4b0;humble_etherborn_bundle_steam;epic_a270c5289b5d4109b1331c84e0d94963;test_6d3078c8912d4d98abc6acc503307e444288669d;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.e8de124d-8354-47ee-a388-e04739df05af;twitch_amzn1.adg.product.e8de124d-8354-47ee-a388-e04739df05af;amazon_8ab8c1c9-564d-ae8e-7c7a-0bd66239ffa5;generic_51152833938695696;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Golazo! Soccer League;Golazo! Soccer League;Golazo! Soccer League;;videos\Golazo Soccer League (2019).mp4;OK;images\Golazo Soccer League (2019).webp;;Amazon;Purple Tree;Klabater;11/09/2019;"Football is all about fun and teamwork. It doesn’t matter if you’re on the field or play it on console sitting with your friends on the couch. Golazo boldly recalls the glory days of the arcade soccer games, bringing back memories of cult classics we all know. With its vintage, not-too-serious, artistic and creative modern approach to classic gameplay, Golazo is certainly a perfect game for people who are weary of football managers or complicated hard-core simulators. You just grab your pad, sit on the couch and play!

Golazo is a dynamic 2.5D arcade football game with a medium sized fields, no fouls and offsides whistled. Just pure fun! Mastering the game is incredibly easy during the fun and furious 7vs7 matches. With its local multiplayer modes and crazy vintage approach, Golazo is the ideal choice for Couch & Party gamers!";Sport, Arcade;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/1431040/313971/f5438348f8119c7d07270d3e230321abef1649dd/1750988143/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1601919566;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.e8e78531-da5e-4651-a75e-357717f42152;psn_CUSA16607_00;xboxone_1788626737;psn_CUSA16589_00;steam_1431040;epic_d29aec5e458544a288f8d9556ea63d56;gog_2029487364;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.e8e78531-da5e-4651-a75e-357717f42152;test_9a1950e523f84acdf291d279f67e49f7e51c68ca;twitch_amzn1.adg.product.e8e78531-da5e-4651-a75e-357717f42152;generic_52629733351304073;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Dungeon of the ENDLESS - Definitive Edition;Dungeon of the ENDLESS - Definitive Edition;Dungeon of the ENDLESS - Definitive Edition;;;OK;images\Dungeon of the ENDLESS - Definitive Edition (2014).webp;;Amazon;Amplitude Studios;Sega, Amplitude Studios;27/10/2014;"Dungeon of the Endless - Definitive Edition

Dungeon of the Endless is Amplitude Studios’ take on the demanding Roguelike genre, mixing in Dungeon-Defense mechanics for a unique gameplay experience.
Condemned to slave labor in the Auriga system as punishment for a life of crime, your situation goes from bad to worse when you crash land in a mazelike Endless facility on an unknown planet.
Your only goal is to survive and get out of there. For that you’ll need a team: inmates, guards, and any survivors have the potential to become great allies.
Explore the facility and unearth life-saving technologies. Your teammates will also need some gear to unleash their true potential and earn powerful abilities. And don’t forget to gather Dust! Without it, you’ll be stuck in the dark.
With monsters at your heels and a merry band of misfits for a team, get ready for a bumpy ride with the Definitive Edition which, along with the base game, includes:

Dungeon of the Endless - Deep Freeze

The “Refreezerator” spaceship will let you experience the game in a different way as well as introduce a new teammate: Kreyang. Don’t touch anything related to Drakken history in her presence… you might lose a hand.

Dungeon of the Endless - Rescue Team

You’ve crashed somewhere in an uncharted part of the galaxy? No one is responding to your cries for help? Fear not, the Rescue Team is on its way! For drill sergeant Sasha, operator Zugma and… Audio engineer Wes, failure is not an option.";Role-playing (RPG), Adventure, Strategy, Indie, Platform, Real Time Strategy (RTS);;;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.e9b762cd-e130-4c5b-aaf5-070d785d1cd2;humble_dungeonoftheendless_definitiveedition_row_steam;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.e9b762cd-e130-4c5b-aaf5-070d785d1cd2;humble_dungeonoftheendless_definitiveedition_storefront_steam_XfE7x;humble_dungeonoftheendless_definitiveedition_storefront_steam_UN6hP;humble_dungeonoftheendless_definitiveedition_storefront_steam_VJTrV;humble_dungeonoftheendless_definitiveedition_storefront_steam_Fw9ZM;humble_dungeonoftheendless_definitiveedition_storefront_steam_vjSXM;generic_56192803307050227;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
