Batman The Telltale Series;Batman: The Telltale Series;Batman The Telltale Series;;videos\Batman The Telltale Series (2016).mp4;OK;images\Batman The Telltale Series (2016).webp;;Amazon;Telltale Games;Telltale Games, LCG Entertainment;02/08/2016;"Batman: The Telltale Series is an episodic graphic adventure game developed by Telltale Games, first released in 2016. The game offers a narrative-focused experience, where players control Bruce Wayne and his alter ego, Batman, making choices that shape the story and relationships with characters.

The plot explores Bruce Wayne’s struggle to uncover corruption in Gotham City, while confronting revelations about his family’s past. The game features dialogue-driven gameplay, quick-time combat, and detective sequences. Decisions carry over across episodes, influencing the narrative’s direction and character arcs.";Adventure, Point-and-click;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/498240/84612/57e570d518eec200de63cde49e33bd14558ff2ed/1750538399/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1482370328;amazon_fa070ce3-b0f8-40f5-aa53-aef28e822093;steam_498240;gog_2140144872;psn_CUSA05332_00;psn_CUSA05603_00;psn_NPWR11243_00;psn_CUSA05598_00;xboxone_360551610;humble_batman_thetelltaleseries_steam;humble_batman_thetelltaleseries_telltale;test_CUSA05332_00;epic_BatfishS2;epic_Batfish;nswitch_0100011005D92000;itch_0319bd59d609d0b4144726e30ffac627e5acd5261ff7968e05c070ad;origin_bc3a95ae157df79d74076202597eea8a1ee84c6a;origin_a5a775baab87aa52040490d622c0c3e225bde3c8ea44cb5c0f33db1ffe8d7d08;discord_255e3e46-f0a3-49f8-9044-6775070984a4;origin_498240;humble_batman_thetelltaleseries_bundle_steam;twitch_fa070ce3-b0f8-40f5-aa53-aef28e822093;test_/batman-the-telltale-series-free-download/;test_batman-the-telltale-series;playfire_batman-the-telltale-series;amazon_fa070ce3-b0f8-40f5-aa53-aef28e822093;test_b28a3f07132dbe7cc791614ac07bf332b952c3f0;test_75e95eec7062d45ad3fd04c9def2db25682d31b4;test_fa709b883be1d666be53b7d990072a9e3d317668;test_b48e0210f1b08be423446869bd872ab881c127bc;test_e3a76553a6c7bdf4af27d661999be9d672edd38a;xboxog_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-2-20211030064527;xboxog_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-2-20211030064825;winstore_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-2-20211030065911;winstore_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-2-20211030070435;winstore_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-3-20211030071538;winstore_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-3-20211030072025;winstore_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-3-20211030072628;winstore_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-3-20211030073222;winstore_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-3-20211102091812;winstore_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-3-20211102094900;winstore_GAME_FROM_