PREY;PREY;PREY;;videos\PREY (2017).mp4;OK;images\PREY (2017).webp;;Epic Games Store;Arkane Studios;Bethesda Softworks;04/05/2017;In Prey, you awaken aboard Talos I, a space station orbiting the moon in the year 2032. You are the key subject of an experiment meant to alter humanity forever – but things have gone terribly wrong. The space station has been overrun by hostile aliens and you are now being hunted. As you dig into the dark secrets of Talos I and your own past, you must survive using the tools found on the station, your wits, weapons, and mind-bending abilities.;Role-playing (RPG), Adventure, Puzzle, Shooter;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/480490/322823/1c0a22c520eef13c6aea7798215d84868c53e848/1750536310/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1726161292;epic_52d88e9a6df248da913c8e99f1e4c526;steam_480490;xboxone_907086072;xboxone_148375255;psn_CUSA06559_00;psn_CUSA04482_00;psn_CUSA04493_00;psn_CUSA06560_00;psn_CUSA07891_00;psn_CUSA07835_00;xboxone_612327918;humble_prey_deluxe_steam;xboxone_1805003112;winstore_9pbc1qfbw563;humble_prey_steam;gog_1158493447;origin_78afd84a2cdb277be88eef1470eb15a9fc017672b6abaa405cab93ffbd913501;origin_2175af491d7f488b09cab3566d3e4834eb882206;gamehouse_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-851-20200408214058;gamehouse_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-851-20200409080600;beamdog_d314218d-c5ba-42db-80bc-0f35f986afd3;discord_2d2274b3-6e23-4bbb-bdb3-f8baf218963d;psn_CUSA08459_00;psn_CUSA08718_00;psn_CUSA08480_00;psn_CUSA08457_00;psn_CUSA08458_00;epic_52d88e9a6df248da913c8e99f1e4c526;beamdog_52d88e9a6df248da913c8e99f1e4c526;beamdog_00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000006272;test_prey;generic_51153514702325325;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Evoland Legendary Edition;Evoland Legendary Edition;Evoland Legendary Edition;;;OK;images\Evoland Legendary Edition (2019).webp;;Epic Games Store;Shiro Games;Shiro Games;07/02/2019;"Evoland Legendary Edition is a compilation of: 
 
- Evoland. 
- Evoland II. 
 
Evoland is a journey through the history of action/adventure gaming, allowing you to unlock new technologies, gameplay systems and graphic upgrades as you progress through the game. Inspired by many cult series that have left their mark in the RPG video gaming culture, Evoland takes you from monochrome to full 3D graphics and from active time battles to real time boss fights, all with plenty of humor and references to many classic games. 
 
Evoland 2 graphics style is changing as you travel through time and its gameplay evolves as you move along the storyline. It is also a real RPG at heart, with a deep scenario based on time travel: explore different eras and change the history of the world. But are you sure that the consequences will not make things worse? 
 
Full of humor and references to classic games, the Evoland series brings a truly epic and extraordinary adventure, unlike anything you’ve ever played before!";Role-playing (RPG), Adventure, Indie;;;epic_530f09c9ac834a7bbc98056c69b44471;gog_1466932507;epic_530f09c9ac834a7bbc98056c69b44471;itch_530f09c9ac834a7bbc98056c69b44471;test_1020470;generic_51985678276052278;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
PlateUp!;PlateUp!;PlateUp!;;videos\PlateUp (2022).mp4;OK;images\PlateUp (2022).webp;;Epic Games Store;It’s happening;Yogscast Games;04/08/2022;Hectic single-player and co-op restaurant management: cook and serve your dishes, upgrade and customise your restaurants, and expand your culinary kingdom with each procedurally-generated location. Work together to cook food, deal with customers, and serve drinks - or do it all yourself!;Strategy, Indie, Simulator;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/1599600/484890/dce6b069ede6b19aa823a43e88aeeb3d13408202/1750705040/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1659620731;epic_541ae054ff3d487caf0a6d7521b66f90;steam_1599600;steam_1613620;humble_plateup_storefront_steam_F596S;humble_plateup_bundle_steam;xboxone_1922695178;humble_plateup_row_bundle_steam;psn_CUSA44827_00;psn_PPSA14232_00;psn_CUSA44826_00;psn_PPSA14231_00;epic_541ae054ff3d487caf0a6d7521b66f90;generic_54449462983384664;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Cultist Simulator;Cultist Simulator;Cultist Simulator;;videos\Cultist Simulator (2018).mp4;OK;images\Cultist Simulator (2018).webp;;Epic Games Store;Weather Factory;Weather Factory;31/05/2018;"Seize forbidden treasures. Summon alien gods. Feed on your disciples.

Cultist Simulator is a game of apocalypse and yearning from Alexis Kennedy, creator of Fallen London and Sunless Sea. Play as a seeker after unholy mysteries, in a 1920s-themed setting of hidden gods and secret histories. Perhaps you're looking for knowledge, or power, or beauty, or revenge. Perhaps you just want the colours beneath the skin of the world.

In this roguelike narrative card game, what you find may transform you forever. Every choice you make, from moment to moment, doesn't just advance the narrative - it also shapes it.

Become a scholar of the unseen arts. Search your dreams for sanity-twisting rituals. Craft tools and summon spirits. Indoctrinate innocents. Seize your place as the herald of a new age.";Role-playing (RPG), Strategy, Simulator;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/718670/157760/e3cb6eaad440da161250db7abadf91f9f57be9d1/1750576673/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1685707057;epic_572811c77f0e4ea0bfc80137dbe6f6dd;steam_718670;gog_1456702644;humble_cultistsimulator_LgCvQ;amazon_051d4284-efb9-42d6-b711-204836d28280;humble_051d4284-efb9-42d6-b711-204836d28280;humble_cultistsimulator_monthly_steam;twitch_051d4284-efb9-42d6-b711-204836d28280;3ds_051d4284-efb9-42d6-b711-204836d28280;humble_cultistsimulator_storefront_steam_a4gH9;test_718670;test_/cultist-simulator-free-download/;test_cultist-simulator;humble_cultistsimulator_bundle_steam;test_45a6e58f83984de160598d008cbebe9588c1b5a2;epic_6b1e73cc05bc412e83f4c636b2d83d77;epic_572811c77f0e4ea0bfc80137dbe6f6dd;amazon_7ffbfb6e-3722-4429-8c21-14c13f258b82;generic_51152722065924302;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Terraforming Mars;Terraforming Mars;Terraforming Mars;;videos\Terraforming Mars (2018).mp4;OK;images\Terraforming Mars (2018).webp;;Epic Games Store;LUCKYHAMMERS Entertainment Inc.;Asmodee Digital;17/10/2018;The taming of the Red Planet has begun! Corporations are competing to transform Mars into a habitable planet by spending vast resources and using innovative technology to raise temperature, create a breathable atmosphere, and make oceans of water. As terraforming progresses, more and more people will immigrate from Earth to live on the Red Planet.;Strategy, Simulator;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/800270/274528/e8924ba159d8bf59b42ab9b66a1763ed1801c2c1/1750585314/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1585571481;epic_582c8940f499450d9033840efe5937a6;steam_800270;humble_terraformingmars_bundle_steam;humble_terraformingmars_steam;discord_0083f7fd-2e66-4c27-aeb2-1b2cad7e6060;gog_2013033253;test_/terraforming-mars-free-download/;test_terraforming-mars;epic_582c8940f499450d9033840efe5937a6;humble_582c8940f499450d9033840efe5937a6;itch_582c8940f499450d9033840efe5937a6;generic_51154330515897727;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
River City Girls;River City Girls;River City Girls;;videos\River City Girls (2019).mp4;OK;images\River City Girls (2019).webp;;Epic Games Store;Arc System Works, WayForward;WayForward;04/09/2019;"River City Girls stars Kyoko and Misako, two street-tough high-schoolers who must fight their way through the six regions of River City to rescue their kidnapped boyfriends, series mainstays Kunio and Riki. Along the way, they'll utilize an arsenal of combos, counters, throws, and special attacks; battle an assortment of enemies; accept numerous side quests; level up with experience points; interact with NPCs (including guest stars from past River City games); and shop for a variety of items, food, and gear to boost stats and unlock new abilities. The girls can even wield weapons and recruit defeated foes to join them in combat!";Adventure, Arcade, Hack and slash/Beat 'em up, Fighting;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/1049320/238102/2d1b54e2d144e556b3f06e8df59fe40cf235ab95/1751181372/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1567695724;epic_588cec64448242d8b61188205d97f887;xboxone_1629043783;steam_1049320;psn_CUSA15878_00;psn_CUSA15834_00;psn_CUSA15883_00;gog_1439166945;psn_CUSA15554_00;humble_rivercitygirls_steam;itch_073e77a936841cb4e2f7aadb5705ecfae42162fbc1787796466a0a9d;itch_XFxSYWlkc2VydmVyXGdcTXkgRHJpdmVcRml0R2lybCBHYW1lc1xSaXZlciBDaXR5IEdpcmxzIFtGaXRHaXJsIFJlcGFja10=;origin_fb68cfa6f533f912d52d3f2abbb9009526caa656;origin_74c4b5735c6464b1c1b7ca6715ab22575e199f24e9815b872d12eb305b8376d8;nswitch_01004E700DFE6000;xboxone_2076503823;test_/river-city-girls-free-download/;test_river-city-girls;nuuvem_b816dacb0a26dd048565127da0b081cbf8205536;psn_PPSA04076_00;psn_PPSA04075_00;fanatical_river-city-girls;humble_rivercitygirls_bundle_steam;nuuvem_d92d0a012bf24b53a377fc95a2477323c64b7255;psn_PPSA04474_00;epic_588cec64448242d8b61188205d97f887;generic_52200467321767460;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
The Vanishing of Ethan Carter Redux;The Vanishing of Ethan Carter;The Vanishing of Ethan Carter Redux;;videos\The Vanishing of Ethan Carter (2014).mp4;OK;images\The Vanishing of Ethan Carter Redux (2015).webp;;Epic Games Store;The Astronauts;Nordic Games Publishing, The Astronauts;25/09/2014;In The Vanishing of Ethan Carter, you play as Paul Prospero, an occult detective who receives a disturbing letter from Ethan Carter and realizes that the boy is in grave danger. When Paul arrives in Ethan's home of Red Creek Valley, he realizes things are even worse than he imagined. Ethan has vanished in the wake of a brutal murder, which Paul comes to see might not be the only murder to investigate. Using both regular and supernatural detective skills, Paul must figure out what happened to the missing boy.;Adventure, Strategy;;no_section;epic_58a6b5e81c644fba8bab2e05137429d9, epic_9447b19ffb6a47e1a654b75178779a28;steam_258520;gog_1207665373;xboxone_54480103;psn_CUSA03048_00;psn_CUSA03130_00;humble_thevanishingofethancarter_steam;humble_thevanishingofethancarter_preorder_steam;test_CUSA03130_00;totalwar_thevanishingofethancarter_steam;d2d_thevanishingofethancarter_steam;psx_The Vanishing of Ethan Carter;humble_thevanishingofethancarter_preorder_gog;test_/the-vanishing-of-ethan-carter-free-download/;test_the-vanishing-of-ethan-carter;epic_9447b19ffb6a47e1a654b75178779a28;test_gfn_102077211;beamdog_00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000008766;beamdog_9447b19ffb6a47e1a654b75178779a28;test_9447b19ffb6a47e1a654b75178779a28;humble_9447b19ffb6a47e1a654b75178779a28;egg_9447b19ffb6a47e1a654b75178779a28;itch_9447b19ffb6a47e1a654b75178779a28;generic_51295405140344828;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Destiny 2;Destiny 2;Destiny 2;;videos\Destiny 2 (2017).mp4;OK;images\Destiny 2 (2017).webp;;Epic Games Store;Bungie;Activision, Bungie;06/09/2017;"In Destiny 2, the last safe city on Earth has fallen and lays in ruins, occupied by a powerful new enemy and his elite army, the Red Legion. Every player creates their own character called a “Guardian,” humanity’s chosen protectors. As a Guardian in Destiny 2, players must master new abilities and weapons to reunite the city’s forces, stand together and fight back to reclaim their home.  
  
In Destiny 2 players will answer this call, embarking on a fresh story filled with new destinations around our solar system to explore, and an expansive amount of activities to discover. There is something for almost every type of gamer in Destiny 2, including gameplay for solo, cooperative and competitive players set within a vast, evolving and exciting universe.";Role-playing (RPG), Adventure, Shooter;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/1085660/718079/b7e668540b5dd0d9885cd03e953ea67d176cd59b/1750614664/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1719265609;epic_592c359fb0e0413fb46dee2d24448eb4;xboxone_144389848;xboxone_245548143;battlenet_1146311730;psn_CUSA06172_00;psn_CUSA08456_00;psn_CUSA05042_00;psn_CUSA05963_00;steam_1085660;humble_destiny2_latam_monthly_blizzardkeys;humble_destiny2_eu_monthly_blizzardkeys;humble_destiny2_me_af_monthly_blizzardkeys;humble_destiny2_asia_monthly_blizzardkeys;humble_destiny2_us_monthly_blizzardkeys;humble_destiny2_beta_bungiekeys;humble_destiny2_rucis_monthly_blizzardkeys;psvita_CUSA05042_00;stadia_Destiny 2;psvita_CUSA08415_00;test_CUSA05042_00;test_CUSA06172_00;discord_1146311730;humble_destiny2_na_blizzardkeys;psn_CUSA08415_00;humble_destiny2_asia_blizzardkeys;stadia_View Destiny 2 Pro.;discord_7a036bbc-e149-4693-8197-3c848615cb58;stadia_20e792017ab34ad89b70dc17a5c72d68rcp1/sku/4950959380034dcda0aecf98f675e11f;stadia_20e792017ab34ad89b70dc17a5c72d68rcp1;humble_destiny2_legendaryedition_row_steam;psn_PPSA02409_00;psn_PPSA02411_00;psn_PPSA02410_00;psn_CUSA08483_00;test_gfn_1085660;test_100362311;test_gfn_100362311;epic_592c359fb0e0413fb46dee2d24448eb4;test_1085660;test_steam_1085660;itch_592c359fb0e0413fb46dee2d24448eb4;battlenet_dst2;generic_51152761107979097;;;;;;;;
