Weird West;Weird West;Weird West;;videos\Weird West (2022).mp4;OK;images\Weird West (2022).webp;;Epic Games Store;Wolfeye Studios;Devolver Digital;31/03/2022;Discover a dark fantasy reimagining of the Wild West where lawmen and gunslingers share the frontier with fantastical creatures. Journey through the origin stories of a group of atypical heroes, written into legend by the decisions you make in an unforgiving land. Each journey is unique and tailored to the actions taken - a series of high stakes stories where everything counts and the world reacts to the choices you make. Form a posse or venture forth alone into an otherworldly confines of the Weird West and make each legend your own.;Role-playing (RPG), Adventure, Indie, Simulator;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/1097350/499142/386f580a84ec11de55147cf7f0a9e2d82c5d0153/1750618800/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1664270844;epic_5ab7c9b39f81481c88dce1e4f106a594;steam_1097350;gog_1421555971;xboxone_2016076229;psn_CUSA17337_00;psn_CUSA17598_00;epic_5ab7c9b39f81481c88dce1e4f106a594;humble_weirdwest_release_steam;psn_PPSA10887_00;psn_PPSA10886_00;itch_2118880;generic_52888803977424130;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Shadowrun Dragonfall - Directors Cut;Shadowrun: Dragonfall - Directors Cut;Shadowrun Dragonfall - Directors Cut;;videos\Shadowrun Dragonfall - Directors Cut (2014).mp4;OK;images\Shadowrun Dragonfall - Directors Cut (2014).webp;;Epic Games Store;Harebrained Schemes;Harebrained Schemes;18/09/2014;Shadowrun: Dragonfall - Director’s Cut is a standalone release of Harebrained Schemes' critically-acclaimed Dragonfall campaign, which first premiered as a major expansion for Shadowrun Returns. The Director's Cut adds a host of new content and enhancements to the original game: 5 all-new missions, alternate endings, new music, a redesigned interface, team customization options, a revamped combat system, and more - making it the definitive version of this one-of-a-kind cyberpunk RPG experience.;Role-playing (RPG), Adventure, Strategy;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/300550/24020/9e7cfe17697a25afa94d482515089c388dde0882/1750503525/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1447363148;epic_5b41454974be4d5883056ba298e53675;steam_300550;gog_1207660913;humble_shadowrun_dragonfall_dc;humble_shadowrun_dragonfall_bundle_steam;ps2_47411;humble_shadowrun_dragonfall_dc_steam;humble_shadowrun_dragonfall_dc_paradox_steam;totalwar_shadowrun_dragonfall_dc_steam;d2d_shadowrun_dragonfall_dc_steam;humble_shadowrun_dragonfall_dc_paradox_keys_restricted_steam;epic_5b41454974be4d5883056ba298e53675;test_5b41454974be4d5883056ba298e53675;test_epic_shadowrundragonfalldirectorscut;test_gfn_100892911;fanatical_shadowrun-dragonfall-directors-cut;test_gfn_300550;xboxone_1939956128;beamdog_00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000007115;humble_5b41454974be4d5883056ba298e53675;psn_PPSA04111_00;psn_CUSA28605_00;psn_CUSA28607_00;psn_PPSA04110_00;beamdog_5b41454974be4d5883056ba298e53675;generic_51154182263000055;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
