DNF Duel;DNF Duel;DNF Duel;;videos\DNF Duel (2022).mp4;OK;images\DNF Duel (2022).webp;;Epic Games Store;Arc System Works, Eighting, Neople;Nexon Co. Ltd.;28/06/2022;"DNF Duel is a fast-paced 2.5D fighting game set in the Dungeon & Fighter universe. Players select from a diverse roster of iconic fighters, each with distinct combat styles, signature skills, and strategic toolsets.

The game combines fluid controls with deep tactical systems, including an MP gauge for powerful abilities and dynamic ""Awakening"" states that can turn the tide of battle. Vibrant stages, eye-catching visuals, and expressive animations bring every clash to life.

With multiple modes — such as Story, Arcade, Survival, Ranked Online, and local versus — DNF Duel caters to both solo players and competitive fighters, offering accessible entry points as well as layers of depth for seasoned players.";Strategy, Fighting;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/1216060/526872/3dadd8812e03b4b78400d568afdd7773fbb3560e/1750643923/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1672824727;epic_82cdbdf05c61474d89c4f9e8a8bf0ea4;psn_CUSA31505_00;psn_PPSA05602_00;psn_PPSA05897_00;psn_CUSA31506_00;psn_PPSA05604_00;psn_CUSA31508_00;steam_1216060;psn_CUSA31740_00;psn_PPSA06164_00;psn_PPSA06168_00;psn_CUSA31739_00;psn_CUSA31507_00;psn_PPSA06169_00;psn_CUSA31742_00;psn_PPSA06170_00;nuuvem_85dd222d0a926f872d983b02405be58a1550710b;nswitch_0100380017D3E000;epic_82cdbdf05c61474d89c4f9e8a8bf0ea4;generic_54954829217861193;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Snakebird Complete;Snakebird Complete;Snakebird Complete;;;OK;images\Snakebird Complete (2023).webp;;Epic Games Store;Noumenon Games;;24/11/2023;A console version of Snakebird that contains both Snakebird and Snakebird Primer and some minor adjustments.;Indie, Puzzle, Arcade;;;epic_8337d1f975514d35ad0c1176e8a29f26;epic_8337d1f975514d35ad0c1176e8a29f26;generic_56284422942773507;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Runbow;Runbow;Runbow;;videos\Runbow (2015).mp4;OK;images\Runbow (2015).webp;;Epic Games Store;13AM Games;Headup Games, 13AM Games, CrossFunction;27/08/2015;"Runbow is an action party game with a unique art style and a never-before seen colour mechanic that will keep you running back for more. Platforms and obstacles appear and disappear as the background colour changes, so if you can’t see something, it doesn’t exist. Whether you're playing alone or with friends, Runbow is fast, frantic, and a lot of fun.

Players can race against each other in The Runbow Run, or go head to head in a number of different modes including King of the Hill and Arena to name a few. Use the Wii U GamePad to become the malevolent ColourMaster controlling the colours and the obstacles in the level, or tackle our toughest game mode, The Bowhemoth, a 30+ minute platforming challenge that will put the patience and skill of even the toughest players to the test.

If dozens of game modes, hundreds of unlockable costumes, and a crazy, colourful gaming challenge sounds like fun, then you better get ready to Runbow!";Adventure, Indie, Platform, Racing;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/464650/79013/652a40929e61839d9233423c45cefdf018c2497a/1751289410/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1478609695;epic_85efb11aaeec4239989113f9a598b372;steam_464650;xboxone_764522213;psn_CUSA08488_00;psn_CUSA07030_00;humble_runbow_wiiu_noa_nintendo;humble_runbow_wiiu_noe_nintendo;psn_CUSA09984_00;humble_runbow_wiiu_nal_nintendo;psn_CUSA09976_00;nwiiu_00050000101D6D00;humble_runbow_steam;humble_runbow_wiiu_noa_unblocked_nintendo;nwiiu_0005000010183000;psn_CUSA12992_00;humble_runbow_wiiu_noe_unblocked_nintendo;humble_runbow_wiiu_nal_unblocked_nintendo;nwiiu_2643c569f3de82fe0e47df246c99e3ec908e64e4;epic_85efb11aaeec4239989113f9a598b372;generic_51154143561650795;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Lifeless Planet Premier Edition;Lifeless Planet: Premier Edition;Lifeless Planet Premier Edition;;videos\Lifeless Planet Premier Edition (2014).mp4;OK;images\Lifeless Planet Premier Edition (2014).webp;;Epic Games Store;Stage 2 Studios;Lace Games, Serenity Forge, Stage 2 Studios;06/06/2014;"While seeking life on a distant planet, an astronaut discovers an abandoned Russian town. He suspects his mission is a hoax until a mysterious young woman saves him from a strange and deadly phenomenon... Lifeless Planet is a third-person action-adventure that features an old-school sci-fi story and spectacular environments in the spirit of classic action-adventures.

After a hard landing on the planet, the astronaut discovers the planet that was reported to be rich with life is instead a barren wasteland. When he goes searching for his crew, he makes a more startling discovery: evidence that humans have already been to this planet years ago! When he comes upon a deserted Soviet-era Russian town, he struggles to make sense of his mission. Did his light-speed travel to the planet send him back in time? Or is this all some strange Cold War hoax?

Along the way, the astronaut meets a Russian woman, Aelita, who is somehow able to survive the hostile atmosphere of the planet. Through an unusual natural phenomenon, her skin causes the soil to glow green under her feet. The player must use these glowing tracks as a guide across the planet past treacherous and deadly threats. Is she leading him to safety... or an untimely death?

Lifeless Planet was inspired by Cold War era science fiction stories, posing questions about humankind's desire for space travel. What if you journeyed across the galaxy to another planet, only to find humans had already been there? What kind of person would sign up for a one-way mission, leaving behind planet Earth and everyone they've ever known and love... to go in search of an Earth-like planet?

Equipped with a limited-use jet-pack and a mobile robotic arm, the player must use wits and skill to solve puzzles, unravel the mystery, and survive the Lifeless Planet!

Key Features:

-Explore 20 unique and atmospheric environments on a vast and treacherous planet.
-Follow a mysterious young woman as she guides you past dangerous terrain and deadly life-forms.
-Investigate the startling discovery of an abandoned Russian town.
