FAR Lone Sails;FAR: Lone Sails;FAR Lone Sails;;videos\FAR Lone Sails (2018).mp4;OK;images\FAR Lone Sails (2018).webp;;Epic Games Store;Okomotive;H2 Interactive Co., Ltd., Mixtvision, Assemble Entertainment;17/05/2018;Far: Lone Sails is a vehicle adventure game. The player needs to maintain and upgrade their unique vessel to traverse a dried-out sea, with the remains of a decaying civilization scattered out on the seabed. Keep your unique vessel going, overcome numerous obstacles and withstand the hazardous weather conditions.;Adventure, Indie, Platform, Puzzle, Simulator;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/609320/152100/cc153147cef6286ac6d7c1121fbba1d7a113f5f7/1750561859/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1521110522;epic_92234289632c4db78116ad21bccdc643;steam_609320;gog_1736537203;xboxone_2036551350;psn_CUSA12901_00;psn_CUSA14846_00;psn_CUSA16034_00;humble_far_lonesails_storefront_steam_yJzbc;discord_a5701e8c-8b58-4b77-8f01-5e1d7ef0bf85;test_/far-lone-sails-free-download/;test_far-lone-sails;playfire_far-lone-sails;epic_92234289632c4db78116ad21bccdc643;fanatical_far-lone-sails;humble_far_lonesails_bundle_steam;generic_51152845285702271;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
