Turmoil;Turmoil;Turmoil;;videos\Turmoil (2016).mp4;OK;images\Turmoil (2016).webp;;Epic Games Store;Gamious;Playdigious, LTGames Global;02/06/2016;Turmoil is a simulation game set during the 19th century oil rush in North America. Get a taste of the rush and rivalry of the time as you earn your way to become a successful oil entrepreneur. As you make money digging up and selling oil, the town will grow along with you. Acquire more town shares than your competitors in a bid to become the new mayor.;Strategy, Indie, Simulator;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/361280/522127/c6c8429b49085740f5312d3d5cbbf5ffebb4f0ec/1750515940/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1671023170;epic_9b1148db19dc457aa1adf9f21ac6f0ff;steam_361280;gog_1812631235;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0003151;humble_turmoil;twitch_9f710b74-9960-4411-bdfc-3cd846ca812c;amazon_9f710b74-9960-4411-bdfc-3cd846ca812c;humble_9f710b74-9960-4411-bdfc-3cd846ca812c;humble_turmoil_steam;3ds_9f710b74-9960-4411-bdfc-3cd846ca812c;humble_turmoil_bundle_steam;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0003151@subscription;steam_1498770;epic_9b1148db19dc457aa1adf9f21ac6f0ff;generic_51295415500500911;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
