ABZU;ABZU;ABZU;;videos\ABZU (2016).mp4;OK;images\ABZU (2016).webp;;Epic Games Store;Giant Squid;505 Games;02/08/2016;"Abzu is an exploration game where you are a lone diver in a lush ocean world. The diver descends deeper and deeper into the depths, where she will encounter majestic creatures, discover ancient secrets, and search for her true purpose. Abzu roughly translates to ""The Ocean of Wisdom"" from ancient Sumerian.";Adventure, Indie, Puzzle;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/384190/74599/ff42f96b297340a395f129ccb906690d82f22f38/1750522199/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1475094707;epic_Curry;steam_384190;gog_1622602219;xboxone_949699803;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0002633;psn_CUSA03364_00;psn_CUSA03349_00;epic_Curry;test_Curry;humble_abzu_steam;humble_abzu_bundle_steam;psvita_CUSA03349_00;xboxone_2143725369;test_CUSA03349_00;epic_7af7476ff9eb4a8d9cd9d6486224de76;itch_ABZU [FitGirl Repack];itch_09c2261141cdf40fc54d3a3cb5570ef2f6413837f6e9c4959f3ff58e;itch_XFxSYWlkc2VydmVyXGdcTXkgRHJpdmVcRml0R2lybCBHYW1lc1xBQlpVIFtGaXRHaXJsIFJlcGFja10=;epic_ABZU [FitGirl Repack];winstore_ABZU [FitGirl Repack];origin_9051542defd5daa778fa8e26322c4f4543296ed5;origin_c7c9b3a154fc97936e9f0035b277f3d7abd39545c791666ecdf73171bc30c7a8;origin_e92f27dd6656af5c157433363c5821f2796955eb6e3878bc0c90e21fa2f982d4;origin_341d3216344149bd7e1826c325e3eb6b97cb326f2b959dcb1f1086a6aee8119d;discord_2b0533ac-8529-46f9-8f0d-2758b533d81e;discord_4e93b4ae-809a-4e82-b974-34e2a70c3e9f;psx_ABZU;steam_steam_384190;test_/abzu-free-pc-download/;test_abzu;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0002633@subscription;beamdog_00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000328;beamdog_Curry;humble_Curry;egg_Curry;psx_CUSA03364_00;itch_Curry;test_sashagame_288;generic_51141384418629514;;;;;;;;;;;;
Transistor;Transistor;Transistor;;videos\Transistor (2014).mp4;OK;images\Transistor (2014).webp;;Epic Games Store;Supergiant Games;Supergiant Games;20/05/2014;An unconventional tactical action RPG in which after a powerful group called the Camerata cause measureless destruction through the ambiguous settlement of Cloudbank, Red, a famous singer in the city, goes on a journey along with her lover who is trapped inside the Transistor, a powerful machine with mysterious properties, to get to the bottom of the situation and get her lost voice back.;Role-playing (RPG), Strategy;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/237930/20996/8b1943f7505da5232c4f37f167006e1a2b9f80f7/1750483205/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1447361955;epic_Dill;steam_237930;gog_1429612159;psn_CUSA00642_00;psn_CUSA00502_00;epic_Dill;test_Dill;psvita_CUSA00502_00;humble_transistor_steam;test_CUSA00642_00;test_CUSA00502_00;humble_transistor_withsoundtrack_steam;epic_bc81d1e7d1794d3a94e4dbf26e92166d;test_237930;test_/transistor-free-download/;test_transistor;playfire_transistor;nswitch_0100BE500BEA2000;generic_51295412943011222;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
