The Stanley Parable;The Stanley Parable;The Stanley Parable;;videos\The Stanley Parable (2013).mp4;OK;images\The Stanley Parable (2013).webp;;Epic Games Store;Galactic Cafe;Galactic Cafe;17/10/2013;The Stanley Parable is a first-person exploration game which ponders questions related to player agency, narrative pacing, escapism through gaming, objective-driven game design, authorial intent, and the conflict of interest between players and game creators.;Adventure, Indie;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/221910/14506/14b3496beeda9c31d1bd99572cc5c5e142887971/1750481711/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1447359219;epic_Freesia;steam_221910;steam_247750;humble_the_stanley_parable_Y53nU;humble_thestanleyparable_steam;humble_thestanleyparable_freedombundle_steam;totalwar_thestanleyparable_steam;d2d_thestanleyparable_steam;epic_Freesia;humble_thestanleyparable_bundle_steam;humble_thestanleyparable_store_steam;test_Freesia;test_/the-stanley-parable-free-download/;test_the-stanley-parable;beamdog_00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000007607;beamdog_Freesia;humble_Freesia;egg_Freesia;itch_Freesia;test_221910;generic_51295404158102079;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Enter the Gungeon;Enter the Gungeon;Enter the Gungeon;;videos\Enter the Gungeon (2016).mp4;OK;images\Enter the Gungeon (2016).webp;;Epic Games Store;Dodge Roll;Devolver Digital;05/04/2016;Enter the Gungeon is a gunfight dungeon crawler following a band of regretful misfits seeking to shoot, loot, dodge roll and table-flip their way to personal absolution by reaching the legendary Gungeon’s ultimate treasure: the gun that can kill the past. Select a hero and battle your way to the bot¬tom of the Gungeon by surviving a challenging and evolving series of floors filled with the dangerously adorable Gundead and fearsome Gungeon bosses armed to the teeth. Gather precious loot, discover hidden secrets, and chat with opportunistic merchants and shopkeepers to purchase powerful items to gain an edge.;Adventure, Indie, Shooter, Arcade;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/311690/216886/11de2f4de6ee112b0ae9c7e7669c2b3c09d56c51/1750506389/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1554472236;epic_Garlic;steam_311690;gog_1456912569;xboxone_401515813;psn_CUSA01659_00;epic_Garlic;psn_CUSA01608_00;uplay_3328;twitch_654f2d8c-54b9-4358-8a4b-05087d8e308b;amazon_654f2d8c-54b9-4358-8a4b-05087d8e308b;3ds_654f2d8c-54b9-4358-8a4b-05087d8e308b;winstore_9nb65s6lfzrt;test_CUSA01608_00;nswitch_01009D60076F6000;humble_enterthegungeon_steam;humble_654f2d8c-54b9-4358-8a4b-05087d8e308b;test_Garlic;test_Some;test_ac84240ad52bbe0dec0e3bbe9db264b2f3302e16;test_/enter-the-gungeon-free-download/;test_enter-the-gungeon;humble_enterthegungeon_us_switch;test_87ac6ce0d52bc8e484c309d9c0c98b428573fee0;test_65cf3887034209c448e74c0caa6affc05874d237;test_epic_enterthegungeon;test_gfn_100818111;test_8556931d5e4dfe9905448f194df5e71e712c705f;test_gfn_311690;beamdog_00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000002793;beamdog_Garlic;humble_Garlic;egg_Garlic;test_gfn_Garlic;test_fdca24d4b12a891c4bc5176df843df7e12f03ec4;psx_CUSA01659_00;test_epic_Garlic;test_100818111;test_2e57ae4350046d0ad7f131ab857864fa7abb5e5a;amazon_36b7a45c-6026-1aef