Oxenfree;Oxenfree;Oxenfree;;videos\Oxenfree (2016).mp4;OK;images\Oxenfree (2016).webp;;Epic Games Store;Night School Studio;Night School Studio;14/01/2016;Oxenfree is a supernatural adventure game. Rites of passage and Senior year traditions set the stage for a group of friends sneaking off to Edwards Island, an old military outpost with no phone service. Players will take on the role of Alex as she brings her new stepbrother Jonas to an overnight party gone horribly wrong. Inspired by classic cult films like Stand by Me and Poltergeist, Oxenfree is an adventure that pulls from the past but looks to the present. “It’s a coming of age story where players control how their hero comes of age,” says Sean Krankel, co-founder of Night School. “We’re drawing on the fond and mortifying aspects of being in your late teens, and setting it against a dangerous and ghostly backdrop.”;Role-playing (RPG), Adventure, Indie;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/388880/47537/5a623af562c607ed9b4cf127be65f65c4cfc0379/1750523747/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1449269998;epic_Hibiscus;steam_388880;gog_1457519353;xboxone_35717019;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0002183;psn_CUSA05051_00;epic_Hibiscus;psn_CUSA04950_00;humble_oxenfree;amazon_7efdcdb3-3a17-48df-bbe2-3bf21919ce2f;humble_7efdcdb3-3a17-48df-bbe2-3bf21919ce2f;twitch_7efdcdb3-3a17-48df-bbe2-3bf21919ce2f;humble_oxenfree_steam;test_CUSA05051_00;3ds_7efdcdb3-3a17-48df-bbe2-3bf21919ce2f;winstore_9nblggh6ctz5;test_CUSA04950_00;humble_oxenfree_bundle_steam;itch_661927;itch_oxenfree;test_661927;test_/oxenfree-free-download/;test_oxenfree;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0002183@subscription;fanatical_oxenfree;test_6deb36790454e13478c0543cc80428e4e8bcba90;humble_oxenfree_dayofthedevsletsgetdigital_bundle_steam;amazon_7561b728-fdbb-4721-8be9-79da05cd8b19;generic_51153461335078687;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Totally Reliable Delivery Service;Totally Reliable Delivery Service;Totally Reliable Delivery Service;;videos\Totally Reliable Delivery Service (2020).mp4;OK;images\Totally Reliable Delivery Service (2020).webp;;Epic Games Store;We're Five Games;tinyBuild;01/04/2020;Delivery Attempted. That's the Totally Reliable Delivery Service guarantee! T.R.D.S. is a ragdoll physics simulation about terrible package delivery couriers. Work together using odd machinery, useful gadgets, and the wonders of physics to reliably deliver packages to their destination.;Adventure, Indie, Simulator, Racing;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/1011670/351743/ed4d3356382a5719c679386e1447344f39c47fbd/1751175979/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1617292978;epic_Hoatzin;steam_1011670;epic_Hoatzin;psn_CUSA18566_00;xboxone_1740172423;psn_CUSA18560_00;test_Hoatzin;test_/totally-reliable-delivery-service-free-download/;test_totally-reliable-delivery-service;steam_1585940;test_gfn_100816111;beamdog_00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000008414;beamdog_Hoatzin;humble_Hoatzin;egg_Hoatzin;humble_totallyreliabledeliveryservice_bundle_steam;generic_51963445924104376;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Darksiders II Deathinitive Edition;Darksiders II: Deathinitive Edition;Darksiders II Deathinitive Edition;;videos\Darksiders II Deathinitive Edition (2015).mp4;OK;images\Darksiders II Deathinitive Edition (2015).webp;;Epic Games Store;THQ Nordic, Gunfire Games, Vigil Games;THQ Nordic;27/10/2015;"A remastered version of the 2012 release, Darksiders II. 
 
Awakened by the End of Days, Death, the most feared of the legendary Four Horsemen, embarks upon a quest to restore mankind, and redeem his brother's name. Along the way, the Horseman discovers that there are far worse things than an earthly Apocalypse, and that an ancient grudge may threaten all of Creation. 
 
Darksiders II follows the exploits of Death, one of the four horsemen of the Apocalypse, in an action-packed tale that runs parallel to the events in the original Darksiders game. This epic journey propels Death across an expansive gameworld as he tries to redeem his brother, War, the horseman blamed for prematurely starting the Apocalypse in Darksiders. 
 
Like the original Darksiders game before it, the second iteration of the series is primarily a hack 'n slash adventure. The game takes place across netherworld environments, including 'The White city', an outpost where angels live, and 'The Eternal Throne', a floating fortress where the Lords of the Dead stand guard over souls that need to be cleansed. Although Death is the most feared of the Four Horsemen, his physical abilities are very different than his brother, War. Death is far more nimble, and relies on a combination of melee and ranged attacks. In combat Death's primary weapon is his huge iconic scythe, with a wide range of other weapons and usable items that must be gathered as the game progresses. Weapons can be dual-wielded, upgradable armor can be acquired for protection and Death has access to his terrifying and powerful mount, Despair.";Role-playing (RPG), Adventure, Puzzle, Hack and slash/Beat 'em up, Fighting;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/388410/45687/eab76d88ce93fcaa8379a3652c9ff6beaf9473c8/1750523509/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1570489975;epic_Hoki;steam_388410;gog_1446463013;xboxone_856892583;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0001234;psn_CUSA02419_00;psn_CUSA02420_00;psn_CUSA05418_00;psn_CUSA08205_00;humble_darksiders2_deathinitiveedition_monthly_steam;twitch_790f3b07-fc9c-4efe-bb66-32bd348a9d23;amazon_790f3b07-fc9c-4efe-bb66-32bd348a9d23;psvita_CUSA02420_00;humble_darksiders2_deathinitiveedition_steam;test_CUSA02420_00;humble_790f3b07-fc9c-4efe-bb66-32bd348a9d23;epic_Hoki;3ds_790f3b07-fc9c-4efe-bb66-32bd348a9d23;test_CUSA02419_00;epic_091d95ea332843498122beee1a786d71;humble_darksiders2_deathinitiveedition_row_steam;humble_darksiders2_deathinitiveedition_conquercovid19_steam;itch_717033ab6b89cd0051e9813ce2b5bf4157594675b06448a3348f4822;origin_ad07ef63f9bf0d256e6e44337a08f7fac8b52a0d;origin_7a97a2f24b95f253753f7e7f924452d1b5a6b9fcd2f2bf40bc37f20225cf0769;test_Hoki;psx_Darksiders II Deathinitive Edition;test_epic_darksidersiideathinitiveedition;