RUINER;RUINER;RUINER;;videos\RUINER (2017).mp4;OK;images\RUINER (2017).webp;;Epic Games Store;Reikon Games;Devolver Digital;26/09/2017;Ruiner is a top-down action shooter created in the spirit of cult cyberpunk anime and game classics. Ruiner is quick and brutal but sophisticated gameplay, original world with mature storyline and unique visual style.;Adventure, Strategy, Indie, Shooter;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/464060/124950/5627c55803f2a1c7ec7a3a14df5a88b6dc3bbcd9/1751289291/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1545788313;epic_Laridae;steam_464060;gog_1637928515;xboxone_93901068;psn_CUSA08386_00;psn_CUSA08417_00;humble_ruiner_monthly_steam;epic_Laridae;winstore_9nlqtdkd0pmt;test_CUSA08417_00;epic_LaridaeStaging;epic_74d82b28ab424956ac24407229fe6faa;itch_5eb48719b7e866fbec1d92c80ebf7c17c35f4c31a871709d224be52c;itch_XFxSYWlkc2VydmVyXGdcTXkgRHJpdmVcRml0R2lybCBHYW1lc1xSVUlORVIgW0ZpdEdpcmwgUmVwYWNrXQ==;origin_8fc2c61c6eab00c2dad6cfb9db37b691d3b08caa;origin_be464865d823640c519693ac32eb584393f24a5587e284450be9fad6fe45457d;humble_ruiner_steam;test_Laridae;test_/ruiner-free-download/;test_ruiner;beamdog_00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000006764;beamdog_Laridae;humble_Laridae;egg_Laridae;itch_Laridae;humble_ruiner_bundle_steam;generic_51154142114559984;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Saints Row The Third Remastered;Saints Row The Third Remastered;Saints Row The Third Remastered;;videos\Saints Row The Third Remastered (2020).mp4;OK;images\Saints Row The Third Remastered (2020).webp;;Epic Games Store;Volition;Deep Silver;22/05/2020;"Saints Row: The Third Remastered gives you control of the Saints at the height of their power, and you live the life to show for it. This is your City. These are your rules.
Remastered with enhanced graphics, Steelport the original city of sin, has never looked so good as it drowns in sex, drugs and guns.
Years after taking Stilwater for their own, the Third Street Saints have evolved from street gang to household brand name, with Saints sneakers, Saints energy drinks and Johnny Gat bobblehead dolls all available at a store near you. The Saints are kings of Stilwater, but their celebrity status has not gone unnoticed. The Syndicate, a legendary criminal fraternity with pawns in play all over the globe, has turned its eye on the Saints and demands tribute.
Refusing to kneel to the Syndicate, you take the fight to Steelport, a once-proud metropolis reduced to a struggling city of sin under Syndicate control. Take a tank skydiving, call in a satellite-targeted airstrike on a Mexican wrestling gang, and fight against a highly-trained military force by your lonesome in the most outlandish gameplay scenarios ever seen.
Weapons of Crass Destruction – It’s one thing to defeat your enemies. It’s another to humiliate them. Hover jets, human cannonball cars and outrageous melee weapons are all part of the fun.
Crazy Character Customisation – Create the most outlandish characters ever seen, from washed-up celebrities to maskless ninja pirates. Inside every sinner, there is a Saint. Who will you become?
Over The Top Co-op – Fly solo or play online with a homie. Give freefall skydiving a try, landing in your partner’s flaming pickup as you make a desperate run toward a heavily armed Syndicate base. Steelport is always more fun with a friend.
All DLC included – All three expansion mission packs and 30 pieces of DLC from the original version.";Adventure, Shooter, Racing;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/978300/365286/ff74714b01f5d61bd5276e7386e43b7062054faa/1750603509/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1620039680;epic_Loon;psn_CUSA14350_00;epic_Loon;psn_CUSA16343_00;test_CUSA16343_00;origin_b0681152e9d1f207036cedba21dfaf3aef911983;humble_saintsrow3_remastered_release_epic_keyless;gog_1435738629;psn_CUSA24182_00;test_/saints-row-the-third-remastered-free-download/;test_saints-row-the-third-remastered;playfire_saints-row-the-third-remastered;steam_978300;psn_PPSA02874_00;psn_PPSA02873_00;humble_saintsrow3_remastered_steam;test_gfn_100398511;humble_saintsrow3_remastered_release_bundle_epic_keyless;beamdog_00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000006799;beamdog_Loon;test_Loon;humble_Loon;egg_Loon;test_FitGirl11;itch_Loon;humble_saintsrow3_remastered_bundle_steam;generic_53229818206464472;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Hob;Hob;Hob;;videos\Hob (2017).mp4;OK;images\Hob (2017).webp;;Epic Games Store;Runic Games;Runic Games;26/09/2017;"Hob is set on a beautiful and dangerous unknown world, with buzzing life above and the whirrs of mysterious machinery below. The more players delve into the world’s design, the more they uncover a planet in peril. Players must learn to survive, understand their true purpose through acquiring skills, and ultimately transform the nature of the world itself.

Hob is presented without text or dialogue. Narrative is revealed as players explore and interact with their mysterious planet, and the strange life forms that inhabit it. Hob features smooth controller gameplay, multi-layered puzzles, and striking visuals.";Adventure, Indie, Platform, Puzzle;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/404680/126695/3d6c36c1f6418ae3224d163bcfe2c17514c6ce33/1751277830/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1507266795;epic_Lyrebird;steam_404680;gog_1300281766;psn_CUSA08319_00;psn_CUSA08079_00;psn_CUSA09862_00;discord_372440317493903380;test_CUSA08319_00;humble_hob_storefront_steam_C3gfi;test_CUSA08079_00;epic_Lyrebird;itch_f1f50449f27530ed35a66d3e9bdd61347ab592144e3b7f7a2c582108;itch_XFxSYWlkc2VydmVyXGdcTXkgRHJpdmVcRml0R2lybCBHYW1lc1xIb2IgW0ZpdEdpcmwgUmVwYWNrXQ==;origin_0e03cb09a3ec3fa945a34a63e8cb36dbf2f614b0;origin_16122d2b71c39eb855ba293b1000f3cebf05c7b445acaed3660955f16ab48cc4;discord_09c33e6f-5962-483a-9a77-9fb5013a3182;test_Lyrebird;fanatical_hob;fanatical_5f20395ee5364e1c835a66ee;test_hob;beamdog_00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000004096;beamdog_Lyrebird;humble_Lyrebird;egg_Lyrebird;itch_Lyrebird;generic_51152974025385052;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
The Witness;The Witness;The Witness;;videos\The Witness (2016).mp4;OK;images\The Witness (2016).webp;;Epic Games Store;Thekla, Inc;Thekla, Inc;26/01/2016;"The Witness is a single-player game in an open world with dozens of locations to explore and over 500 puzzles. This game respects you as an intelligent player and it treats your time as precious. There's no filler; each of those puzzles brings its own new idea into the mix. So, this is a game full of ideas.";Adventure, Indie, Puzzle;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/210970/48606/d91f43a3b3d871e8650a876391fb620985cf7cda/1751248980/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1453238896;epic_Magnolia;steam_210970;gog_1461060839;xboxone_193310209;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0002584;psn_CUSA04263_00;psn_CUSA00498_00;epic_Magnolia;humble_the_witness_jG26B;test_Magnolia;humble_thewitness_freedombundle_steam;psvita_CUSA00498_00;humble_thewitness_monthly_steam;test_CUSA00498_00;humble_thewitness_storefront_steam_Rx2Ey;test_CUSA04263_00;humble_thewitness_conquercovid19_steam;origin_f550f7305b2cbfe0247b7cfd27dc355c43dc3d8a7261df73b29fecaaeda27d44;origin_ea6e537455af7c6c94f99de414692a8716c4c343;discord_44a383e3-9f50-43e7-bf76-3b69dad2e90a;psx_CUSA04263_00;humble_thewitness_humblehealcovid19_steam;generic_51295405654131801;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
INSIDE;INSIDE;INSIDE;;videos\INSIDE (2016).mp4;OK;images\INSIDE (2016).webp;;Epic Games Store;Playdead;Playdead;29/06/2016;Inside is a first person horror game. Developed by 9ine and released on Jul 29th, 2012;Adventure, Indie, Platform, Puzzle;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/304430/270913/f44db3dc6a15962e2f7c2905f32bcdee959717d3/1750504200/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1584103602;epic_Marigold;steam_304430;gog_1916896012;xboxone_885488152;steam_959940;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0001941;psn_CUSA02754_00;psn_CUSA05297_00;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0002901;epic_Marigold;humble_inside_monthly_steam;humble_inside_bundle_steam;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0001941@subscription;generic_51152992411696483;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Ghostbusters The Video Game Remastered;Ghostbusters The Video Game Remastered;Ghostbusters The Video Game Remastered;;videos\Ghostbusters The Video Game Remastered (2019).mp4;OK;images\Ghostbusters The Video Game Remastered (2019).webp;;Epic Games Store;Saber Interactive;Mad Dog Games, LLC;03/10/2019;Hunt, fight and trap a variety of new and familiar ghouls and phantasms, all remastered in HD resolution. Ghostbusters: The Video Game Remastered equips you with cool gadgets and upgradeable weapons to play with in huge boss fights and destructible environments. Scan and analyze targets with the P.K.E. Meter and Paragoggles, then strap on your Proton Pack to wear ghosts down with the blast stream before wrangling them with the capture stream.;Adventure, Shooter;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/1449280/319001/e023edef1dd9f63efdc807edb965eaeda0df26ef/1750689933/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1604391275;epic_Mint;epic_Mint;epic_MintDummy;xboxone_1700344676;psn_CUSA15493_00;psn_CUSA15558_00;psn_CUSA17156_00;humble_ghostbusters_thevideogame_remastered_epic_keyless;humble_ghostbusters_steam;nswitch_0100EAE00D9EC000;steam_1449280;test_/ghostbusters-the-video-game-remastered-free-download/;test_ghostbusters-the-video-game-remastered;test_Mint;psn_CUSA18170_00;beamdog_00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000003429;beamdog_Mint;humble_Mint;egg_Mint;itch_Mint;humble_ghostbusters_thevideogame_remastered_bundle_steam;generic_52319039574777376;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Sundered Eldritch Edition;Sundered Eldritch Edition;Sundered Eldritch Edition;;videos\Sundered Eldritch Edition (2017).mp4;OK;images\Sundered Eldritch Edition (2017).webp;;Epic Games Store;Thunder Lotus;Thunder Lotus;28/07/2017;Sundered is a horrifying fight for survival and sanity, a hand­-drawn epic from the ​creators of ​Jotun. You play Eshe, a wanderer in a ruined world, trapped in ever­-changing caverns teeming with eldritch horrors. Harness the power of corrupted relics to defeat gigantic bosses, at the cost of your humanity.;Adventure, Indie, Platform;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/535480/201555/e605b6fb22ebef01564f8ec39be93aa5418e139c/1751299493/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1683300019;epic_Moa;steam_535480;gog_1116941879;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0003249;psn_CUSA08136_00;psn_CUSA07282_00;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0002349;uplay_10684;xboxone_1892393976;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0003649;humble_sundered_monthly_steam;test_CUSA07282_00;epic_Moa;humble_sundered_steam;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0002330;epic_ca8077d80493497188e0ca5bca3ebe60;stadia_5ec4424b963f44d18d0016322c19c9f0rcp1;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0002352;test_sundered;playfire_sundered;humble_sundered_bundle_steam;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0002349@subscription;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0003249@subscription;itch_664936;humble_Moa;beamdog_Moa;beamdog_00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000007747;gog_2085474562;generic_51154283433164514;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Super Meat Boy Forever;Super Meat Boy Forever;Super Meat Boy Forever;;videos\Super Meat Boy Forever (2020).mp4;OK;images\Super Meat Boy Forever (2020).webp;;Epic Games Store;Team Meat;Team Meat, Thunderful;23/12/2020;"Meat Boy and Bandage Girl have grown as a couple since 2010. It seems like only yesterday the two love birds were escaping from an exploding laboratory in the sky. Now it’s the current year, and they’ve welcomed their daughter Nugget into the world. Their peaceful days enjoying life as a family came to an abrupt end when Dr. Fetus beat the snot out of them with a rusty shovel, and kidnapped Nugget! Now it’s up to Meat Boy and Bandage Girl to rescue their daughter from a lunatic fetus in a jar that can only be described as an incel version of Tony Stark.

- Super Meat Boy Forever is the sequel to Super Meat Boy! This is a new experience that eclipses the original. Don’t stare directly at it unless you still have your eclipse glasses.
- 7200 individually handcrafted levels combine dynamically to give you a new challenge every single time you play. Seven thousand two hundred levels. They said we couldn’t do it, but we did. Who’s they? Don’t ask. They don’t like it when you ask.
- It’s hard, but fair. Nothing in life worth having comes easy. Just ask Dark Soulman.
- Meat Boy and Bandage Girl can fight back. It’s time to unleash the raw fury of parenthood on their foes just like Liam Neeson in that documentary about his family vacation in Paris.
- Bigger boss battles than before. Your mind will be blown. Your socks will be blown off. Team Meat is not liable for any of this.
- Brand new art with stunning detail and resolution. There are a lot of pixels in here. Grab the biggest display you have and watch those dots change color rapidly with gumption. Don’t sit too close though. (If your parents aren’t home you can sit as close as you want we won’t tell, but Team Meat is still not liable for any of this.)
- A soundtrack composed by Ridiculon so intense that the state of Wyoming has issued a ban on all audio devices capable of playing it out of fear that just a single note will cause the dormant super volcano beneath Yellowstone to erupt ushering in a new age of darkness.
- Frame by frame artisan crafted in game animations, and animated cutscenes that will make you experience procedurally generated emotions.
- A story so rich and moving that it makes Citizen Kane look like an unboxing video for a dehumidifier.";Adventure, Indie, Platform, Puzzle;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/581660/430389/4f1aa576764333212df37564c9b2dd7abe0ac849/1751305068/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1641786618;epic_Moose;steam_581660;nes_47680;epic_MooseDummy;epic_Moose;test_/super-meat-boy-forever-free-download/;test_super-meat-boy-forever;playfire_super-meat-boy-forever;xboxone_2059797788;psn_CUSA27278_00;psn_CUSA16602_00;snes_47680;humble_supermeatboyforever_bundle_steam;nswitch_01009C200D60E000;generic_51154291442212746;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
