The Eternal Cylinder;The Eternal Cylinder;The Eternal Cylinder;;videos\The Eternal Cylinder (2021).mp4;OK;images\The Eternal Cylinder (2021).webp;;Epic Games Store;ACE Team;Good Shepherd Entertainment;30/09/2021;In The Eternal Cylinder, players control a herd of adorable creatures called Trebhums and must explore a strange alien world filled with exotic lifeforms, surreal environments, and the constant threat of the Cylinder, a gargantuan rolling structure of ancient origin which crushes everything in its path. This unique ecosystem is a massive, procedurally generated land with unique animal AI, real-time world destruction, and organic exploration and puzzle design to create emergent gameplay that ensures no two playthroughs are ever the same.;Adventure;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/865680/498604/534f43fb89a35ce0276b155181656f35ac0362df/1750591025/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1665679686;epic_Oriole;epic_OriolePartnerStaging;epic_Oriole;xboxone_1647672528;epic_OrioleDummy;psn_CUSA13108_00;xboxone_1821165740;psn_CUSA13143_00;steam_865680;psn_PPSA06369_00;psn_PPSA06368_00;epic_e31ea2e684624c32b64621d29e451c63;humble_theeternalcylinder_storefront_steam_3aM48;humble_theeternalcylinder_bundle_steam;generic_52543127556172397;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
