Unreal Tournament;Unreal Tournament;Unreal Tournament;;;OK;images\Unreal Tournament (2016).webp;;Epic Games Store;Epic Games;Epic Games;01/05/2016;"Unreal Tournament is a first-person shooter video game developed by Epic Games. It was to be the ninth installment in the Unreal franchise, and the first main entry in the series since Unreal Tournament 3 (2007). The game utilizes Epic's Unreal Engine 4 and was to be released for free on Microsoft Windows, OS X, and Linux.

Unreal Tournament's development is crowdsourced and open to contribution from anyone. Epic Games has been using forums for discussions and Twitch livestreams for regular updates. The source code of the game is published on GitHub.";Shooter;;;epic_UnrealTournamentDev;epic_UnrealTournamentDev;epic_Zen_4.14;epic_InfiltratorDemo_4.22;epic_UnrealTournamentPublicTest;epic_UnrealTournamentDevPlaytest;ps2_SLES-50074;epic_UnrealTournamentEditor;epic_UnrealTournamentEditorPublicTest;beamdog_00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000008660;beamdog_UnrealTournamentDev;humble_UnrealTournamentDev;egg_UnrealTournamentDev;ps2_Unreal Tournament;generic_51295418915358934;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Rebel Galaxy;Rebel Galaxy;Rebel Galaxy;;videos\Rebel Galaxy (2015).mp4;OK;images\Rebel Galaxy (2015).webp;;Epic Games Store;Double Damage Games;Double Damage Games;20/10/2015;Rebel Galaxy is an action-packed, swashbuckling space opera. You’ll battle pirates, explore anomalies, befriend aliens, scavenge battle wreckage, mine asteroids, and discover artifacts. Choose your path as a roguish do-gooder, crafty space-trader or power-hungry privateer - or maybe a little of each! Buy larger and more powerful craft with your hard-earned credits, and outfit them with a variety of wicked weapons and defenses. Set in a galaxy of fantastic sights, and secrets to be found, Rebel Galaxy is above all a space epic of adventure, exploration, and combat.;Role-playing (RPG), Adventure, Strategy, Indie, Simulator;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/290300/43186/ea106a4155fc86888ead4428ca9bebf5e3951c52/1750500989/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1447378125;epic_Weaver;steam_290300;gog_1435582019;xboxone_126264108;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0002166;psn_CUSA02586_00;psn_CUSA02381_00;epic_Weaver;psn_CUSA06668_00;psvita_CUSA02381_00;humble_rebelgalaxy_steam;test_CUSA02586_00;test_CUSA02381_00;psx_Rebel Galaxy;test_Weaver;test_/rebel-galaxy-free-download/;test_rebel-galaxy;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0002166@subscription;fanatical_rebel-galaxy;beamdog_00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000006449;beamdog_Weaver;humble_Weaver;egg_Weaver;itch_Weaver;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0002166@xgp_vault_game;generic_51154105680330054;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
