Gamedec;Gamedec;Gamedec;;videos\Gamedec (2021).mp4;OK;images\Gamedec (2021).webp;;Epic Games Store;Anshar Studios;Anshar Publishing;16/09/2021;Gamedec is an adaptive cyberpunk RPG. As a private detective, it’s your job to solve crimes inside virtual worlds. What decisions will you make in a world where child slavery is a F2P game, where murder over a game-clan dispute is an every-day reality? Who will you become in the XXII century?;Role-playing (RPG), Adventure, Indie, Puzzle, Point-and-click;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/917720/500662/48156060c5bebb2d4125d230396bc06c2f1b42f5/1750595922/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1708698972;epic_a01150ee6deb406c92dd2b2445186163;steam_917720;gog_1921398290;discord_fa63024e-bd9b-4107-9271-121a30ffb0be;gog_1326749904;epic_a01150ee6deb406c92dd2b2445186163;humble_gamedec_storefront_steam_p8rsq;humble_gamedec;humble_gamedec_choice_steam;psn_PPSA12363_00;generic_52522866326050554;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Five Nights at Freddy's Into the Pit;Five Nights at Freddy's: Into the Pit;Five Nights at Freddy's Into the Pit;;videos\Five Nights at Freddys Into the Pit (2024).mp4;OK;images\Five Nights at Freddys Into the Pit (2024).webp;;Epic Games Store;Mega Cat Studios;Mega Cat Studios;07/08/2024;"Jump into the pit and immerse yourself in a new chapter in the Five Nights at Freddy’s universe. Oswald wishes his town, and his life, weren’t so boring. That all changes when he explores the ball pit in a rundown pizzeria and finds himself in the past. However, Oswald’s deepest desire will have an unexpected cost…

Survive five nights of terror in this chilling adventure game. Travel between time periods, gather clues, and outrun the threat relentlessly pursuing you. Move swiftly and stay hidden, and you may just survive. But be careful—it’s not just your own life that’s on the line. Oswald’s father and children from the past could all meet their end if you don’t save them.";Adventure, Indie, Puzzle;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/2638370/737287/bd0d416f957fcc97aac7570f96b8d1c7cd792fb0/1750817777/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1723065416;epic_a0fbc3eb950341e290ae20a7d02cc501;steam_2638370;xboxone_1835944487;epic_a0fbc3eb950341e290ae20a7d02cc501;generic_57248431181653962;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Chessarama;Chessarama;Chessarama;;videos\Chessarama (2023).mp4;OK;images\Chessarama (2023).webp;;Epic Games Store;Minimol Games;Minimol Games, Hawthorn Games;05/12/2023;Chessarama is a collection of chess-inspired puzzle and strategy games that use chess pieces and their established move sets, then reimagines their goals and themes. Solve challenges, unlock collectibles, and compete against each other on the leaderboards. Welcome to Chessarama!;Strategy, Turn-based strategy (TBS), Indie, Puzzle, Tactical, Card & Board Game;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/1831830/635703/b0ef03b2636de023dda6ded18ac31c1fcc37470d/1751036306/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1701661036;epic_a1292bca78514801bc03571e9247909d;steam_1831830;xboxone_1751868147;epic_a1292bca78514801bc03571e9247909d;generic_55481609142422612;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Kerbal Space Program;Kerbal Space Program;Kerbal Space Program;;videos\Kerbal Space Program (2015).mp4;OK;images\Kerbal Space Program (2015).webp;;Epic Games Store;Squad;Private Division;27/04/2015;In Kerbal Space Program, take charge of the space program for the alien race known as the Kerbals. You have access to an array of parts to assemble fully-functional spacecraft that flies (or doesn’t) based on realistic aerodynamic and orbital physics. Launch your Kerbal crew into orbit and beyond (while keeping them alive) to explore moons and planets in the Kerbol solar system, constructing bases and space stations to expand the reach of your expedition.;Indie, Simulator;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/220200/171271/78c61bd83ebdcf9bfd985dc8dd77db6c4e272a9d/1750481505/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1530546317;epic_a1e2ce30defe4a9187ebc14fc9d2bd8b;steam_220200;gog_1429864849;xboxone_632819091;steam_231410;steam_steam_220200;psn_CUSA04780_00;humble_kerbalspaceprogram_row_monthly_steam;humble_kerbalspaceprogram_steam;humble_kerbalspaceprogram_rucis_monthly_steam;itch_8edc336a36d98d71b16df2ee6bb60c407ea69415bf6243334678d2e1;itch_XFxSYWlkc2VydmVyXGdcTXkgRHJpdmVcRml0R2lybCBHYW1lc1xLZXJiYWwgU3BhY2UgUHJvZ3JhbSBbRml0R2lybCBSZXBhY2td;origin_b0130308000556b18f4ffaeb581b4e55db7958d3;origin_6cd087338da533a270b65b6eb73ad8cb6ef8fc5aec30e586667b4b2ed65563b7;humble_kerbalspaceprogram_fightforjustice_steam;test_220200;test_/kerbal-space-program-free-download/;test_kerbal-space-program;test_4bf4590139086d5c8b98b0192761216d59175aa4;test_173e46af17692e4f81583d2a8468a2297d4592d7;test_5ec84517240b5dccad9868752d7c72320bf521bc;test_935447eae78dba8e027e4e226f98b7585e6bb922;test_afaef9ea4b2a242fc691fce794c33b3598710f94;test_1cc413c6543b55dc412ff168ecf39f538a2d96c0;test_e4ad81383a542c5cd504501e51955a5ff60b7f1f;humble_kerbalspaceprogram_bundle_steam;humble_kerbalspaceprogram_standwithukraine_row_bundle_steam;humble_kerbalspaceprogram_standwithukraine_cn_bundle_steam;epic_a1e2ce30defe4a9187ebc14fc9d2bd8b;itch_a1e2ce30defe4a9187ebc14fc9d2bd8b;generic_51153174990624383;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Black Widow Recharged;Black Widow: Recharged;Black Widow Recharged;;videos\Black Widow Recharged (2021).mp4;OK;images\Black Widow Recharged (2021).webp;;Epic Games Store;Nickervision Studios;Atari, Inc.;27/10/2021;The original cult classic arachnid-starring, twin-stick shooter returns! Just in time for Halloween, Black Widow: Recharged has been reimagined for modern gameplay, with vibrant visuals, powerful new abilities, and another original soundtrack from award-winning video game composer Megan McDuffee. Aim for a high score in the old school arcade mode and earn bragging rights with your name at the top of the leaderboard. Or test your skills and rank on the boards in one of 30 intensely creative challenges, which twist the gameplay in new and exciting ways. Collect cash from downed enemies to charge a powerful web blast, or pick up one of a dozen new power-ups including explosive blasts, spread-shots, and fear, trapping all enemies in your web. Every mode and level is playable in local co-op mode with a friend.;Shooter, Arcade;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/1714180/404993/1d7378d5686eb64e7a4b9ea4b8dc56fefb2cbafa/1751022844/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1632922232;epic_a21fd90517bf428eb7c995a8c3261722;steam_1714180;epic_a21fd90517bf428eb7c995a8c3261722;xboxone_1730600743;psn_CUSA30369_00;psn_PPSA05256_00;psn_PPSA05255_00;beamdog_00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000001314;beamdog_a21fd90517bf428eb7c995a8c3261722;test_a21fd90517bf428eb7c995a8c3261722;humble_a21fd90517bf428eb7c995a8c3261722;egg_a21fd90517bf428eb7c995a8c3261722;gog_2038976793;humble_blackwidow_recharged_bundle_steam;generic_54814493887519809;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Neon Abyss;Neon Abyss;Neon Abyss;;videos\Neon Abyss (2020).mp4;OK;images\Neon Abyss (2020).webp;;Epic Games Store;Veewo Games;Team17, Yooreka Studio;13/07/2020;"Neon Abyss is a frantic, roguelike action-platformer where you run ‘n’ gun your way into the Abyss as part of the Hades formed ‘Grim Squad’. Featuring unlimited item synergies and a unique dungeon evolution system, each run diversifies the experience and every choice alters the ruleset. Get ready to unleash hell!

Combining furious run ‘n’ gun action and deep, roguelike mechanics, Neon Abyss pits you as a member of the ‘Grim Squad’ – a task force set-up by Hades himself to infiltrate the Abyss and defeat the New Gods. Death is not the end as every time you die, you’ll find yourself more empowered than before.";Role-playing (RPG), Adventure, Indie, Platform, Shooter;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/788100/298247/f1a98b8f868c6946fcada2084cd6770dc25f2695/1750584286/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1594714631;epic_a26f991a5e6c4e9c9572fc200cbea47f;steam_788100;itch_349726;gog_1743370862;xboxone_1802006334;xboxone_1882004205;psn_CUSA18917_00;psn_CUSA18931_00;humble_neonabyss_row_steam;epic_a26f991a5e6c4e9c9572fc200cbea47f;humble_neonabyss_row_postlaunch_steam;test_/neon-abyss-free-download/;test_neon-abyss;humble_neonabyss_choice_steam;humble_neonabyss;fanatical_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-4-20211031074339;fanatical_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-4-20211031081221;fanatical_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-3-20211031081810;fanatical_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-3-20211031084204;fanatical_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-3-20211031093937;fanatical_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-3-20211101143308;fanatical_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-3-20211101145422;fanatical_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-3-20211101155422;fanatical_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-3-20211101165422;fanatical_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-3-20211101175422;fanatical_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-3-20211101185422;fanatical_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-3-20211101195422;fanatical_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-3-20211101233423;fanatical_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-3-20211102003423;fanatical_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-3-20211102013423;fanatical_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-3-20211102084900;fanatical_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-3-20211102094900;fanatical_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-3-20211102104900;fanatical_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-3-20211102114900;fanatical_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-3-20211102124900;fanatical_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-3-20211102134901;fanatical_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-3-20211102144901;fanatical_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-3-20211102154901;fanatical_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-3-20211102164901;fanatical_GAME