Use cunning strategy and tactics to tame and ride the many dinosaurs and other primeval creatures roaming the dynamic, persistent ecosystems across land, sea, air, and even underground. Build your character’s strengths and gain items, skills, and pet creatures using in-depth role-playing systems. Start a tribe with hundreds of other players to survive and dominate competing tribes...and ultimately discover the ARK’s true purpose.";Role-playing (RPG), Adventure, Indie, Shooter, Simulator;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/346110/372586/b23204cd58f68c42a07248e8472b9296c1c875c5/1750513376/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1622089232;epic_aafc587fbf654758802c8e41e4fb3255;steam_346110;xboxone_983730484;psn_CUSA06782_00;psn_CUSA06676_00;psn_CUSA08806_00;humble_ark_survivalevolved_steam;winstore_9nblggh52xc6;itch_69b271992afd66a728dca449b51bb9dfec475d66a26a2cf16bb7c040;origin_99e491b40d9aa7d54d79839280304d456f52fcd4;origin_0c4f616d5518f52036b72933ff0071f57cd445ecc5fcf42e24898d0ef2e79004;epic_aafc587fbf654758802c8e41e4fb3255;origin_412035;test_aafc587fbf654758802c8e41e4fb3255;steam_steam_346110;test_/ark-survival-evolved-free-download/;test_ark-survival-evolved;playfire_ark-survival-evolved;test_steam_arksurvivalevolved;test_epic_arksurvivalevolved;test_gfn_100809011;test_gfn_346110;beamdog_00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000963;beamdog_aafc587fbf654758802c8e41e4fb3255;humble_aafc587fbf654758802c8e41e4fb3255;egg_aafc587fbf654758802c8e41e4fb3255;test_gfn_18541011;test_gfn_aafc587fbf654758802c8e41e4fb3255;epic_deaeb7a174e74a10b1caa9a5dc1d7697;epic_c8100452cf954e2292152d17182386ff;test_346110;test_steam_346110;test_18541011;itch_aafc587fbf654758802c8e41e4fb3255;generic_51141387560247467;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
