Frostpunk;Frostpunk;Frostpunk;;videos\Frostpunk (2018).mp4;OK;images\Frostpunk (2018).webp;;Epic Games Store;11 bit studios;11 bit studios;24/04/2018;"Frostpunk, the newest title from the creators of This War of Mine, is a society survival game where heat means life and every decision comes at a price. In an entirely frozen world, people develop steam-powered technology to oppose the overwhelming cold. You face the task of building the last city on Earth and securing the means necessary for your community to survive.

Optimization and resource management often clash with empathy and thoughtful decision-making. While city and society management will consume most of the ruler’s time, at some point exploration of the outside world is necessary to understand its history and present state.";Strategy, Indie, Simulator;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/323190/553817/d7f470c4d5519f83e39504df2c22449dc3ee6974/1750508483/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1685028532;epic_b2e00fc16632475782a7730d1bd7cb60;steam_323190;gog_1648559910;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0003547;xboxone_2075703134;psn_CUSA15690_00;psn_CUSA15716_00;humble_frostpunk_storefront_steam_LAUXc;humble_frostpunk_choice_steam;winstore_9ns0kh25d76x;itch_eb83f8d7ec90e6e6ed417c8e686ede761197ad0e0b437b3e5b03bb49;itch_XFxSYWlkc2VydmVyXGdcTXkgRHJpdmVcRml0R2lybCBHYW1lc1xGcm9zdHB1bmsgW0ZpdEdpcmwgUmVwYWNrXQ==;origin_49b8df52ecd4d4f455fda69d614a1a8e44f13b18;origin_98cad37dcb25e3e690e958e6e3d12fdb5c6b14c7856812c41020e169a3bb1c54;discord_1bb082e9-ef07-4a97-bd37-ead4294e5bc9;humble_frostpunk;psn_CUSA18311_00;test_323190;test_/frostpunk-pc-11-download/;test_frostpunk;playfire_frostpunk;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0003547@subscription;epic_b2e00fc16632475782a7730d1bd7cb60;test_epic_frostpunk;test_gfn_101894911;test_gfn_323190;beamdog_00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000003288;beamdog_b2e00fc16632475782a7730d1bd7cb60;test_b2e00fc16632475782a7730d1bd7cb60;humble_b2e00fc16632475782a7730d1bd7cb60;egg_b2e00fc16632475782a7730d1bd7cb60;humble_frostpunk_bundle_steam;itch_b2e00fc16632475782a7730d1bd7cb60;generic_51152889843856351;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Relicta;Relicta;Relicta;;videos\Relicta (2020).mp4;OK;images\Relicta (2020).webp;;Epic Games Store;Mighty Polygon;Ravenscourt, Koch Media;03/08/2020;"Relicta is a first-person physics-based puzzle game where you need to creatively combine magnetism and gravity in order to unravel the secrets of Chandra Base. Alone in the treacherous depths of the Moon, your scientific mind is the only thing that can keep your daughter alive… 
 
Play as a top physicist stranded on an eerie, derelict Moon base. Find your way around the enigmatic, terraformed craters by bending gravity and magnetism to your will in order to solve physical puzzles. Will you rush straight ahead and try to reach safety - or will you take your time to gather clues and unravel the intrigues of 22nd century orbital politics? Buried in the eternal darkness of the lunar craters lies a secret that might claim your daughter’s life - or change the fate of humanity forever. Are you ready to face the ultimate consequences of your research?";Adventure, Indie, Puzzle;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/941570/309893/ca78cb98d73994ce1c146059ab92c31f94727810/1751166778/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1599224956;epic_b4670484aae24db492f0b468a98fe361;steam_941570;gog_1784456497;xboxone_1618309410;psn_CUSA17918_00;psn_CUSA17538_00;epic_b4670484aae24db492f0b468a98fe361;gog_1488365382;test_/relicta-free-download/;test_relicta;humble_relicta_storefront_steam_dZ70Q;humble_relicta;humble_relicta_choioce_steam;itch_b4670484aae24db492f0b468a98fe361;generic_51604776201625949;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Remnant From the Ashes;Remnant: From the Ashes;Remnant From the Ashes;;videos\Remnant From the Ashes (2019).mp4;OK;images\Remnant From the Ashes (2019).webp;;Epic Games Store;Gunfire Games;Perfect World Entertainment, Intragames;20/08/2019;"The world is in ruins. Only a remnant of mankind remains, hunted to near extinction by horrors from another world. As one of the few survivors left, you will venture into portals to fantastic realms to gather the resources and firepower needed to fight back and retake what was lost.

Remnant: From the Ashes is a third-person survival-action game set in a post-apocalyptic world overrun by mythical creatures. The game provides players and up to three of their friends with a unique, customizable gameplay experience filled with intense shooting and melee combat, gear and weapon crafting, character progression and dynamically-generated levels that offer an infinite number of ways to explore and take on deadly monsters and epic bosses.";Role-playing (RPG), Adventure, Shooter;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/617290/217524/9b6cf513df3664a23890473fd0cf18d52e77fcbd/1750562993/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1554857990;epic_b4a0d2d15acb4db894a599b810297543;steam_617290;xboxone_2056655762;psn_CUSA10507_00;psn_CUSA13830_00;psn_CUSA18442_00;itch_e80eaaa55ce8b2e970228eb0bf549c15b917242c30268c331259be71;origin_00d085b67351a4cb0b7bfa4953033d84de975771;origin_897f156c22c8ebe70dd07d8f286eb3644c4d46b3d5ce7c8febae168be0da0b36;discord_259494e3-659e-44fc-81ec-3d86b57f4880;psn_CUSA18971_00;epic_b4a0d2d15acb4db894a599b810297543;test_/remnant-from-the-ashes-free-download/;test_remnant-from-the-ashes;playfire_remnant-from-the-ashes;test_epic_remnantfromtheashes;test_gfn_100864811;beamdog_00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000006484;beamdog_b4a0d2d15acb4db894a599b810297543;test_b4a0d2d15acb4db894a599b810297543;humble_b4a0d2d15acb4db894a599b810297543;egg_b4a0d2d15acb4db894a599b810297543;test_epic_b4a0d2d15acb4db894a599b810297543;test_100864811;itch_b4a0d2d15acb4db894a599b810297543;humble_remnant_fromtheashes_steam;humble_remnant_fromtheashes_bundle_steam;generic_51390342244921088;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Nioh The Complete Edition;Nioh: The Complete Edition;Nioh The Complete Edition;;videos\Nioh The Complete Edition (2017).mp4;OK;images\Nioh The Complete Edition (2017).webp;;Epic Games Store;Team NINJA;Sony Interactive Entertainment, Koei Tecmo Games;07/11/2017;"Ready to die? Experience the newest brutal action game from Team NINJA and Koei Tecmo Games. In the age of samurai, a lone traveler lands on the shores of Japan. He must fight his way through the vicious warriors and supernatural Yokai that infest the land in order to find that which he seeks. 
 
