Dungeon of the Endless Apogee;Dungeon of the Endless: Apogee;Dungeon of the Endless Apogee;;;OK;images\Dungeon of the Endless Apogee (2021).webp;;Epic Games Store;Playdigious;Playdigious;22/01/2021;Dungeon of the Endless: Apogee is the award-winning Rogue-Like Dungeon-Defense game, in which you and your team of heroes must protect the generator of your crashed ship while exploring an ever-expanding dungeon, all while facing waves of monsters and special events as you try to find your way out. The Apogee Edition of Dungeon Of The Endless includes the full game and five DLCs.;Role-playing (RPG), Adventure, Strategy;;;epic_b5e9c6a18ace4bf9b76253a65f2f070c;epic_b5e9c6a18ace4bf9b76253a65f2f070c;epic_d27b5714582b46ef8bf6f765aed59fe8;generic_54810303196219036;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Atari Mania;Atari Mania;Atari Mania;;videos\Atari Mania (2022).mp4;OK;images\Atari Mania (2022).webp;;Epic Games Store;Illogika Studios;Atari, Inc.;13/10/2022;A wild journey through videogame history, Atari Mania is a microgame collection wrapped in an hilarious retro-driven narrative of exploration and surprise.;Adventure, Arcade;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/1911800/504559/ce89d9ef0423ea1ec8ad385e271f1ffed12615b2/1751494669/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1665674090;epic_b74fd85fc1af47019e4e7a065694141d;steam_1911800;epic_b74fd85fc1af47019e4e7a065694141d;psn_PPSA12640_00;psn_PPSA12641_00;psn_CUSA39601_00;generic_55803078186644704;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Doodle Devil Dark Side;Doodle Devil: Dark Side;Doodle Devil Dark Side;;;OK;images\Doodle Devil Dark Side (2025).webp;;Epic Games Store;JoyBits;JoyBits;19/08/2025;"The Power of Destruction is in Your Hands!

While Doodle God was creating light, life, and balance, Doodle Devil was quietly crafting chaos, temptation, and sin.

Step into the shadows in this wickedly addictive puzzle game where you mix and match elements not to build, but to corrupt. The same clever mechanics and creative exploration that made Doodle God a worldwide hit return - only now, every combination leads you deeper into the darker side of existence.

Discover the Seven Deadly Sins. Create demons, monsters, and the horrors of war. Spread disease, greed, and despair across a crumbling world. From zombie apocalypses to nuclear catastrophes, your imagination is the only limit to destruction.

With every tap, you shape a universe of evil, unlocking twisted new elements, dark humor, and morally questionable outcomes. But remember - being bad has never been so much fun.";Indie, Puzzle, Simulator;;;epic_b75f769b59e14d48b57d4fb773f33446;epic_b75f769b59e14d48b57d4fb773f33446;epic_521bf8fc16894f61b85a89335eae5e6d;generic_59367756883378227;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
