Cities Skylines;Cities: Skylines;Cities Skylines;;videos\Cities Skylines (2015).mp4;OK;images\Cities Skylines (2015).webp;;Epic Games Store;Colossal Order;Paradox Interactive;10/03/2015;Cities: Skylines is a modern take on the classic city simulation genre. The game introduces new game play elements to realize the thrill and hardships of creating and maintaining a real city whilst expanding on some well-established tropes of the city building experience. From the makers of the Cities in Motion franchise, the game boasts a fully realized transport system. It also includes the ability to mod the game to suit your play style as a fine counter balance to the layered and challenging simulation. You're only limited by your imagination, so take control and reach for the sky!;Strategy, Simulator;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/255710/285736/c6d0fd84c7635300ea7ce0ca9222840f47fe228d/1750489550/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1589550020;epic_bcbc03d8812a44c18f41cf7d5f849265;steam_255710;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0002824;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0002835;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0002844;psn_CUSA06407_00;psn_CUSA06548_00;uplay_1890;psn_CUSA09498_00;humble_cities_skylines_steam;humble_citiesskylines_bundle_row_steam;humble_citiesskylines_bundle_latam_steam;humble_citiesskylines_bundle_rucis_steam;test_CUSA06407_00;winstore_9nwvc7xp3pfd;humble_cities_skylines_preorder_steam;itch_c983fcfecc3c5b99b20c0da0ed87d49aa9203982c5b01af833dcde69;itch_XFxSYWlkc2VydmVyXGdcTXkgRHJpdmVcRml0R2lybCBHYW1lc1xDaXRpZXMgLSBTa3lsaW5lcyBbRml0R2lybCBSZXBhY2td;origin_e4f7c5df93a0cd10b1b9520b1fa8765cbe146eae;origin_591cff4b15e23467d0ab263d04af34ac774c43a6d00d4793a5ffdd2bf66aa7fe;humble_citiesskylines_row_bundle_steam;psx_Cities: Skylines;test_CUSA06548_00;test_255710;epic_bcbc03d8812a44c18f41cf7d5f849265;test_/cities-skylines-free-download/;test_cities-skylines;playfire_cities-skylines;test_bcbc03d8812a44c18f41cf7d5f849265;humble_cities_skylines_initial_ru_steam;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0002824@subscription;test_e